/* Words To Live By: Part Two — fetched from thevolumesoftruth.com */
var WTLB_TWO = [{"id":"introduction","num":1,"title":"Introduction","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"**WORDS TO LIVE BY**\n\n**PART TWO**"},{"align":"center","text":"_More Words of Wisdom\n\nFrom The Lord, Our God and Savior_\n\n\n\n\n\nFor all those who have dedicated\n\nThemselves to Me by means of The Truth,\n\nThose who have recognized My words\n\nAnd also do them..."},{"align":"center","text":"Those who came to Me empty\n\nThat I might fill them up,\n\nThat they might be truly dedicated to Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Even as I had dedicated Myself to them also,\n\nThat we may become one..."},{"align":"center","text":"Set apart in My glory, for My glory,\n\nTo the joy of their Father in Heaven..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua.\n\n\n\n\n\nGrow wise in Me, and live according to My Word,\n\nEven according to all these Letters I have given you,\n\nBy which I have set all these crooked paths straight.\n\nFor My every word is Scripture, My every Letter truth."},{"align":"center","text":"For it is written:\n\n_Man shall not live by bread alone,\n\nBut by every word that proceeds\n\nFrom the mouth of God {{ref:Matthew 4:4}}..._"},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"i-am-the-lord-s","num":2,"title":"I Am The Lord's","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"**A Prayer Against Temptation**"},{"align":"center","text":"I am The Lord’s!\n\nAnd I will no more give myself to diverse lusts,\n\nTo the cares and deceits of my flesh and this world."},{"align":"center","text":"I am The Lord's!\n\nMy heart, it is The Lord’s; My mind, it is The Lord’s;\n\nMy will, it is The Lord’s; My flesh, it is The Lord’s;\n\nThe whole of my body, even all I am, I give to The Lord."},{"align":"center","text":"I am The Lord’s!\n\nYea, I pour out my life before The Lord,\n\nEven as He poured out His; let me receive it!\n\nIn the name of My Love, I call out\n\nIn YahuShua’s name, I ask to receive it!"},{"align":"center","text":"YahuShua, My Life and My Righteousness,\n\nI want Your life!"},{"align":"center","text":"My Lord and my God, I am yours!\n\nDo with me as You please, according to\n\nThe good pleasure of Your will..."},{"align":"center","text":"I give myself away..."},{"align":"center","text":"Amen."}]},{"id":"the-bridegroom-approaches","num":3,"title":"The Bridegroom Approaches","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Thus says The Lord: I AM COME!…\n\n\n\nFrom the farthest reaches of creation tothe deepest depths of the earth, below the foundations, from beyond time and space shall the sound of My voice come forth! IT SHALL RESOUND LOUDLY! I SHALL BE HEARD!\n\nEven within the hearts of men shall My voice burst forth, rushing through their veins, causing each of their members to tingle, a great and wonderful shudder within their spirits to the purging of their souls!\n\n\n\nFor I sit higher than the tallest mountain, I am set high above the highest heavens, set apart and holy, set apart in power and great glory!\n\n\n\nBehold, before the beginning was My glory declared, and from the ends of time was My majesty set amongst the stars! Before the earth was made, I wore the universe as a garment!\n\nWho is like Me?! Declares The Alpha. Who holds all existence together by the Word of His power and by the vastness of His knowledge? Says The Omega.\nAnswer, young children, answer if you know. Speak My name aloud; withhold not! SHOUT, MY SONS AND DAUGHTERS! Let your hearts burst forth with praise! Let every beat resound within your chests, to the praise of My glory!\n\nBless the name of pure, unending love! Bless the name of mercy and grace, the name of righteousness! Bless the name of Him who bore your sins upon the tree! KISS THE SON! Says YAHUWAH, The Holy! Kiss Him upon His feet, kiss Him upon His hands, put your hand in His side–TASTE and see! Come close, and kiss My wounds which I received, yes, each one you gave Me. Kiss Me, and be separated no longer; partake of His fullness and receive of Me!\n\n\n\nAwaken your hearts! Rouse from your slumber! YOUR KING COMES TO YOU! He is just, HE is your salvation! His garment is righteousness! Have you grasped it? Hurry, lay hold on Him!\n\nHe is My heart, says The Father. Press your ear against My chest, and listen to the sound of My love, every beat of My mercy. Feel the embrace of My arms, strong and gentle–I AM YOUR FATHER! Your heart’s one embrace!\n\n\n\nMy children, have you heard? Have you truly considered? THE DESIRE OF AGES IS COME! Therefore sing, sing for Me!...\n\n\n\nTHE BRIDEGROOM APPROACHES!"}]},{"id":"the-only-way","num":4,"title":"The Only Way","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved children, I say this once again, so you may be saved: Come out! _Come out from among them and be separate! Says The Lord. And no more touch what is unclean, and I will receive you! {{ref:2 Corinthians 6:17}}_"},{"align":"center","text":"For there is but One Way!..."},{"align":"center","text":"YahuShua HaMashiach,\n\nYes, He who is called Jesus The Christ,\n\nHE is The Only Way!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore follow close behind Him,\n\nIn His very footsteps,\n\nAnd you shall surely live and not die..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord whose dominion is everlasting\n\nAnd whose authority is absolute,\n\nThe Only Lord God of Hosts, The I AM."}]},{"id":"wake-up","num":5,"title":"Wake Up","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Wake up and pay attention!\n\nAwaken out of this sleep, be shaken out\n\nOf this slumber, and call upon My name!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Seek out My will that you may know it;\n\nHeed the sound of this Trumpet and prepare!..."},{"align":"center","text":"For My Kingdom comes, and My will\n\nShall be done on earth as in Heaven..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord God."}]},{"id":"hold-fast","num":6,"title":"Hold Fast","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, prepare your hearts\n\nAnd do not abandon hope..."},{"align":"center","text":"Though much death draws near and\n\nThe pain of death increases in every corner,\n\nThough heavy sorrows overtake the land\n\nAnd tears fill your eyes, hold fast..."},{"align":"center","text":"Embrace Me fully and do not waver..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"splendor","num":7,"title":"Splendor","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I created autumn so all may\nPartake of My brushstrokes,\n\nAnd know I am God, and give Me glory..."},{"align":"center","text":"For My splendor is written\n\nIn the leaves of the trees;\n\nIt is carried upon the wind,\n\nAs it moves through the tall grasses;\n\nIt soars high above on the wings of eagles,\n\nYet remains as near as the fragile flower at your feet..."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, everywhere you look,\n\nThe hand of God is clearly seen..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"in-the-image-of-god","num":8,"title":"In The Image of God","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"All have sinned and fall short of the Glory of God; there is none righteous, no, not one. And for this reason YahuShua The Messiah was sent to die for all men; thereby freeing mankind from the chains which held him captive, loosing him from the bonds which bound him to the punishment of sin, which is death."},{"align":"center","text":"So then as The Messiah was\n\nCrucified and died, and is risen,\n\nSo too must you crucify your life of old..."},{"align":"center","text":"Who you were must perish,\n\nAlong with your sinful ways,\n\nThen shall you truly be born again..."},{"align":"center","text":"Revived and restored in The Image of God..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"life-is","num":9,"title":"LIFE IS","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Blessed be the name of The One\n\nWho is, and was, and is forevermore,\n\nThe Fosterer and Protector of those\n\nTossed away in bitter ignorance..."},{"align":"center","text":"For LIFE IS, before its very conception..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"a-gemstone","num":10,"title":"A Gemstone","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Like a gemstone shining in the midst of all\n\nThis darkness, easily found by the eyes of God,\n\nSo shall you be in the day you surrender your life,\n\nThe day you give up this fight and return to Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"no-walls","num":11,"title":"No Walls","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"No church named of men\n\nIs the true church - not one..."},{"align":"center","text":"Rather each member individually,\n\nWho believes in The Messiah and obeys\n\nHis voice, in whom His spirit dwells,\n\nMake up the True Church of His body..."},{"align":"center","text":"No walls, only spirit and truth..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"marriage","num":12,"title":"Marriage","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I gave unto man woman,\n\nFrom his side did I form her,\n\nAnd he who was one became two;\n\nAnd behold, the two became one again in marriage..."},{"align":"center","text":"Two of one flesh, man and woman {{ref:Genesis 2:21-24}}..."},{"align":"center","text":"And I saw that it was very good..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"bitter","num":13,"title":"Bitter","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"If you dispense the food of God to the hungry,\n\nWhile using your own salt to salt that which\n\nHas salt in itself, will not the food you offer\n\nLose its flavor and become bitter in the mouths\n\nOf those who came looking to be fed?..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"gone-from-this-place","num":14,"title":"Gone From This Place","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The Thief shall enter the house\n\nAnd steal away all who are not tied down,\n\nFastened, or shackled to the house..."},{"align":"center","text":"And all those in whom He sees of Himself\n\nShall surely be gone from this place!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"a-modest-answer","num":15,"title":"A Modest Answer","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Saying “I don’t know” is truthful,\n\nHumble, a modest answer..."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet assertions without knowledge are akin\n\nTo a lie, the seeds of pride and vanity..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"sanctuary","num":16,"title":"Sanctuary","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Come out from among them,\n\nAnd take refuge in Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am your only shelter,\n\nYour only sanctuary from the storm..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Holy One of Israel."}]},{"id":"bless-those-who-curse-you","num":17,"title":"Bless Those Who Curse You","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"My children, struggle not against the principles of another, nor rebuke them with your own words, nor correct them by your own understanding. Let go of your personal notions of right and wrong, and strive to love others in spite of yourselves, and have compassion for those with whom you disagree."},{"align":"center","text":"Do not judge them,\n\nNor shun them in your heart..."},{"align":"center","text":"_Rather love those who speak against you,_\n\nBecause you obey My Word..."},{"align":"center","text":"_Bless those who curse you,_\n\n_And pray for those who mistreat you,_\n\n_As it is written {{ref:Matthew 5:44}}..._"},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-only-faithful-and-true-witness","num":18,"title":"The Only Faithful and True Witness","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I have written it on tablets of stone\n\nAnd within the heart of man, and within\n\nThe pages of My Book it is made plain;\n\nThus they are without excuse..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am God alone, The Righteous One..."},{"align":"center","text":"I alone am holy, just and good;\n\nI alone have divided right from wrong;\n\nI alone have established\n\nThe Law and define what is sin;\n\nBehold, I expose the darkness and bring\n\nAll hidden things into the light..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I alone sit as Judge,\n\nThe Only Faithful and True Witness..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"created-anew","num":19,"title":"Created Anew","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Trust in Me, and you shall be set free..."},{"align":"center","text":"For it is the humble,\n\nPenitent man who shall see God;\n\nBehold, he shall look upon My face,\n\nAs I restore him in My image..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am the image of The Invisible God,\n\nThe perfect reflection of The Father,\n\nThe face of The Majesty from on high,\n\nImmanu El..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore open your heart to Me,\n\nAnd I shall create you anew..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"humble-and-penitent","num":20,"title":"Humble and Penitent","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"All upon the earth who have gained maturity\n\nHave become so very poor and desolate..."},{"align":"center","text":"For once you were wealthy,\n\nRich beyond words, for then you knew\n\nThe Kingdom of Heaven as a child;\n\nYet now you are grown, your light\n\nQuickly fading, as the ways of this\n\nWorld pull you down to the pit..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore return to Me, humble and penitent;\n\nCome to Me as a child..."},{"align":"center","text":"For by no other means shall you pass through {{ref:Matthew 18:3-4}}..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-pure-of-heart","num":21,"title":"The Pure of Heart","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"What is a child’s inheritance on earth and in Heaven, if the years of their life be few in number and they remain in their innocence? Assuredly, I say to you, they will inherit The Kingdom of Heaven, for The Father holds the pure of heart in the palm of His right hand. For like the firefly which alights upon the tall grass, so are these little ones, precious lights shining among men."},{"align":"center","text":"And though the little ones may suffer\n\nAt the hands of men in this world,\n\nI tell you the truth, all arrive at\n\nThe Father’s house in a moment,\n\nIn the twinkling of an eye..."},{"align":"center","text":"Where healing is complete\n\nAnd every tear is wiped away,\n\nThe ways of the world and men forgotten..."},{"align":"center","text":"Only love abides, as they look upon\n\nThe face of their Father forever..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"rest","num":22,"title":"Rest","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Many things shall be put to rest in\n\nThe Lord’s Day, even death and the grave;\n\nDestruction shall have no place,\n\nAnd evil shall be far removed..."},{"align":"center","text":"_For as it is written:_\n\n_They shall not hurt nor destroy in all_\n\n_My Holy Mountain, for the earth shall be_\n\n_Full of the knowledge of The Lord_\n\n_As the waters cover the sea {{ref:Isaiah 11:9}}..._"},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, beloved ones, pray always\n\nThat you are counted worthy to\n\nEnter My rest, that you may abide\n\nIn the presence of The Lord, forever..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"your-only-salvation","num":23,"title":"Your Only Salvation","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"O most foolish and deceived generation,\n\nCan anyone cut out their own heart and live?..."},{"align":"center","text":"And who is able to walk alone in darkness,\n\nWithout a light to guide them?\n\nWho shall uphold them when they stumble\n\nOr catch them when they fall?\n\nWho will bind up their wounds?..."},{"align":"center","text":"O ignorant and confused generation,\n\nDeceived peoples, The Stone which you seek\n\nTo cast off is LIFE, your only salvation!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"your-help-and-your-shield","num":24,"title":"Your Help and Your Shield","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The Mashiach is your help and your shield..."},{"align":"center","text":"YahuShua, whom you call Jesus and Christ,\n\nIs The Rock of your Salvation,\n\nThe One who is and was and is to come;\n\nFor The Father and The Son are One..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore embrace Me in My Mercy,\n\nAnd receive of Me in My Great Love..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord God."}]},{"id":"the-lord-s-table","num":25,"title":"The Lord’s Table","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The Lord’s table is a bounty..."},{"align":"center","text":"And those who eat from My plate are\n\nAlways full, and those who drink from\n\nMy cup shall never go thirsty..."},{"align":"center","text":"For My cup overflows,\n\nBearing fruit in every part of your life,\n\nBringing forth love and understanding..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"the-sign-of-the-son-of-man","num":26,"title":"The Sign of The Son of Man","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The heavens shall be divided,\n\nAnd divided again, the glory thereof\n\nStretching from the earth to heaven,\n\nAnd the clouds shall be rolled back like a scroll..."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold the brilliance, O earth!\n\nBe bowed down and weep, O sons of men!\n\nFor The One whom you pierced is about to appear! {{ref:Zechariah 12:10}}..."},{"align":"center","text":"Let every eye be opened therefore,\n\nLet all in the earth see, until the fullness\n\nOf the revelation is made complete..."},{"align":"center","text":"Thus that which was the beginning and the end\n\nShall also be the end which brings forth\n\nThe new beginning..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"soiled","num":27,"title":"Soiled","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The water of the earth can only cleanse\n\nThat which is soiled on the skin;\n\nBy no means can it cleanse\n\nThat which is soiled in the spirit..."},{"align":"center","text":"This is reserved for the blood of The Lamb..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"against-god","num":28,"title":"Against God","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"That which is unnatural is universally known,\n\nThough the men and women of this world deny it;\n\nAnd that which is against God shall be purged by fire..."},{"align":"center","text":"Even all that offends shall be destroyed\n\nAnd come to a swift end..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"walk-with-me","num":29,"title":"Walk With Me","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"My Word is for all who truly seek Me\n\nAnd long to know My ways,\n\nEven to walk in them..."},{"align":"center","text":"Thus My Word can only be accepted\n\nAnd understood by those who have\n\nReceived the love of the Truth,\n\nFor they abide in Me and\n\nMy spirit resides within them..."},{"align":"center","text":"For how can one who stands\n\nApart from Me know Me?\n\nAnd how can one who teaches his\n\nOwn way walk with Me in Mine?..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-water-of-siloam","num":30,"title":"The Water of Siloam","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Men do not have understanding of the Scriptures in themselves. Rather it is a gift from God, received through the Holy Spirit, given to those who have placed all their trust in The Holy One, embracing Me as I truly am. Or have you never read this Scripture: _The fear of The Lord is the beginning of wisdom, and the knowledge of The Holy One is understanding? {{ref:Proverbs 9:10}}_\n\nTherefore to those who have received is all revealed, and to those who have not received is all shut away. Shall the darkness understand the light? For only those of The Light, bathed in His glory, shall see - the rest left blinded."},{"align":"center","text":"For until one calls on the name of\n\nThe Messiah, in sincerity and in truth,\n\nBy no means shall they receive..."},{"align":"center","text":"_For He is The One who had placed_\n\n_The mud upon their eyes to heal them..._"},{"align":"center","text":"_Behold, He is also The Water of Siloam_\n\n_Which was sent to wash them,_\n\n_That they might now see {{ref:John 9:6-7}}..._"},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-perfect-reflection","num":31,"title":"The Perfect Reflection","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Apart from Me, there is no wisdom! Apart from The Holy One, there is no life! Apart from The Vine, there are no branches!\n\nBehold, the leaves wither and the fruit has been cast down, for the people have no favor with God. Thus every dry branch must be broken off and cast into the fire, all corrupt fruit must be left and tread down.\n\nFor the temple of God has lost its form; its comeliness has departed, every chamber is empty. For the heart of man is void, his countenance unyielding. Thus the pride of man has become a chasm, both deep and wide."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore repent, and receive of Me\n\nAs I am, and not as you would have Me be,\n\nThat you may be truly born again."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am the perfect reflection of The Father,\n\nThe image of The Invisible God..."},{"align":"center","text":"I died, behold, I am risen,\n\nAnd by My life are you saved;\n\nThat you might become the perfect\n\nReflection of Me, The One alone\n\nIn whom is everlasting life..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"my-body-my-bride","num":32,"title":"My Body, My Bride","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"My church has no walls,\n\nAnd is called by no other name except\n\nThe name The Father has given Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Its members are of one mind\n\nAnd one spirit, of one love,\n\nOne flock with one Shepherd..."},{"align":"center","text":"A people set apart who keep\n\nThe Commandments of The Father\n\nAnd remain faithful to The Son,\n\nStriving always to walk in My ways..."},{"align":"center","text":"For those who truly know Me\n\nDwell in Me, and I in them;\n\nFor they are Mine, even as I am theirs also..."},{"align":"center","text":"My body, My bride..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"the-remnant","num":33,"title":"The Remnant","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I am He who searches the hearts\n\nAnd minds, I know My own;\n\nI know whose love is steadfast,\n\nWhose faith is unmoving..."},{"align":"center","text":"And this is the True Church\n\nMy people long for, the remnant\n\nWhich now is and is yet to come..."},{"align":"center","text":"For it is not found outwardly in the world,\n\nBut inwardly, in the temple of God..."},{"align":"center","text":"I AM THE LORD."}]},{"id":"the-truth","num":34,"title":"The Truth","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The Scriptures are not malleable;\n\nThe Commandments do not change!..."},{"align":"center","text":"For The Truth is absolute,\n\nForever standing on a hill,\n\nBright and shining,\n\nImmovable, unbreakable!..."},{"align":"center","text":"The Everlasting Stone which has\n\nBecome The Head of the Corner {{ref:Matthew 21:42}},\n\nThe Great Mountain which fills the whole earth {{ref:Daniel 2:35}}..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"absolute","num":35,"title":"Absolute","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The Word stands forever..."},{"align":"center","text":"Immovable and everlasting,\n\nUnchangeable, having complete\n\nAuthority over all things,\n\nThe light and the dark,\n\nThe righteous and the wicked..."},{"align":"center","text":"Indeed, the whole universe is\n\nSet within the confines of His will,\n\nGiving heed to Him who created it,\n\nForever and ever..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"twin-daggers","num":36,"title":"Twin Daggers","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"My words are fire, singeing the forehead\n\nOf the arrogant, setting the countenance\n\nOf the prideful ablaze, twin daggers\n\nPiercing the heart of every hearer..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore hear the Word of The Lord,\n\nAnd heed the call..."},{"align":"center","text":"For it is a call to repentance, a shout\n\nAnd a witness, a proclamation of Truth..."},{"align":"center","text":"A trumpet of alarm and war, a declaration\n\nOf judgment, a strong rebuke..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"abolished","num":37,"title":"Abolished","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The reign of evil shall be abolished,\n\nThe wicked stricken and the evil of heart\n\nBlotted out, extinguished in the\n\nLake of My burning heart..."},{"align":"center","text":"For My heart is set ablaze in My anger,\n\nAnd My countenance burns like a raging fire;\n\nMy sadness is infinite, the weight of\n\nUnending sorrow covers Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"For as I live, says The Lord, I take no\n\nPleasure in the destruction of the wicked..."},{"align":"center","text":"But call all in the earth to repent,\n\nTo turn from their evil ways\n\nAnd return to Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"every-heart-laid-bare","num":38,"title":"Every Heart Laid Bare","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"One Commandment broken are all Commandments broken. One sin committed in The Messiah’s name are all sins accounted to you. One sin repented in His name, all are forgiven you. For I know your thoughts, My children, even your innermost intentions, and I know whether or not you are fully converted in your hearts.\n\nAnd though you may lie to yourselves, and bear false witness in the sight of many witnesses, nothing is hidden from the eyes of God - every lie exposed, every heart laid bare, in the Day I rise up and judge the earth."},{"align":"center","text":"Come to Me, therefore, in sincerity and in truth;\n\nHumble yourselves in The Messiah’s name..."},{"align":"center","text":"For He is The True Light, utterly void of darkness,\n\nThe Only Way to follow, The Truth Absolute;\n\nBy Him alone shall you walk into everlasting life..."},{"align":"center","text":"For only those who walk in Him shall find Me,\n\nAnd only those in union with Him shall know Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-only-true-religion","num":39,"title":"The Only True Religion","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I am The Way, The Truth, and The Life..."},{"align":"center","text":"And this is pure, undefiled love,\n\nThe only means by which The Law\n\nOf The Father may be fulfilled:\n\nYou shall love The Lord your God\n\nWith all your heart, with all your mind,\n\nWith all your soul and with all your strength;\n\nAnd yes, beloved, you shall love\n\nYour neighbor as yourself..."},{"align":"center","text":"For this is to walk in Me, this is to abide in Me,\n\nThe only true religion in which is life..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"true-faith","num":40,"title":"True Faith","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"True faith has a name,\n\nAnd true religion yields fruit of the same..."},{"align":"center","text":"A Bride who obeys the voice of her\n\nHusband and walks in His ways,\n\nA people worthy to be called by His name..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"regain-the-line","num":41,"title":"Regain the Line","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, turn aside and come to Me."},{"align":"center","text":"Regain the line and together we shall walk,\n\nChoosing the good and refusing the evil,\n\nUntil you also have forgotten your sin."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, it is separated from you\n\nAs far as the east is from the west..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"worthless-images","num":42,"title":"Worthless Images","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Do not put your trust in idols, nor in any man-made image forged of stone or marble, or of wood or brass, gold or of fine metal; there is no life in it! For they can not speak or walk; they have no power at all.\n\nYea, men bear them upon their shoulders, for they can not move from their places. They have no strength, they are helpless, worthless images carved in futility and must be borne."},{"align":"center","text":"Look how easily they are toppled\n\nBy the wind and broken in pieces,\n\nWhen the earth is shaken but a little..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"impotent-leaders","num":43,"title":"Impotent Leaders","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Do not put your trust in any man,\n\nThough he speaks with a clever tongue,\n\nWith many enticing words of unity\n\nAnd peace, and many great promises..."},{"align":"center","text":"And though others bow down to him\n\nAnd give him glory, you shall not\n\nPlace your trust in any man..."},{"align":"center","text":"For man is but flesh..."},{"align":"center","text":"Easily crushed beneath the weight\n\nOf a single branch falling from a tree..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-prince-of-peace","num":44,"title":"The Prince of Peace","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"YahuShua HaMashiach\n\nIs The Fulfillment of all things,\n\nThe Truth and Understanding you seek,\n\nThe Meaning of Life..."},{"align":"center","text":"HE is The Bread which came down\n\nFrom Heaven to feed those who hunger,\n\nThe Fountain of Living Waters for those\n\nWho thirst, The Prince of Peace..."},{"align":"center","text":"The ONLY Way, The ONLY Truth,\n\nThe ONLY Life..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord God."}]},{"id":"the-goal","num":45,"title":"The Goal","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The spirit of The Law is shown\n\nIn The Messiah’s vesture, He being the\n\nSame One who taught you The Law anew,\n\nBy His example and by His every word and deed..."},{"align":"center","text":"For The Law is fulfilled in The Messiah;\n\nIndeed, He is the goal at which the Torah aims {{ref:Romans 10:4}}..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord God."}]},{"id":"life-without-end","num":46,"title":"Life Without End","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"My mercy endures forever..."},{"align":"center","text":"And those who receive of My Mercy\n\nShall likewise endure, forever..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"cherished","num":47,"title":"Cherished","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The works of men are evil, even from their youth..."},{"align":"center","text":"Thus the little children shall be\n\nMy inheritance, and the babes My jewels..."},{"align":"center","text":"For the innocent come forth as lights shining\n\nOut of darkness, gifts born from the womb;\n\nThey are precious; to be cherished\n\nIs every child in their youth..."},{"align":"center","text":"For the innocent are of more value\n\nThan gold and silver, prized\n\nAbove precious stones..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"one","num":48,"title":"ONE","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Give heed to My words and understand. For as I had spoken to My friends in times past, so now do I also speak to you. For the time has come and is coming and is already here, when all signs and wonders shall be made manifest, when all prophecy shall be fulfilled.\nRejoice, for your redemption draws near! And though the time of great sorrows has come in, hold fast, for these days shall be shortened... _No more pain, no more tears, no more death, all sorrows passing away, rebirth, a time of refreshing which shall never end._"},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, remember My words and have peace:"},{"align":"center","text":"One God...\n\n\n\nOne Son, The Only Way to The Father..."},{"align":"center","text":"One Truth, One Word, One Messiah, One Spirit;\n\nOne Food, One Bread and One Drink..."},{"align":"center","text":"One Body..."},{"align":"center","text":"Of which I am all,\n\nThe All in All..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"take-your-fill","num":49,"title":"Take Your Fill","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Come and drink fully of that which is sweet;\n\nCome and drink also of that which you perceive\n\nTo be bitter and very hard to swallow..."},{"align":"center","text":"Ingest it fully..."},{"align":"center","text":"For it too shall become sweet\n\nWhen understanding comes..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"more-than-the-asking","num":50,"title":"More Than the Asking","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Repentance is more than the asking..."},{"align":"center","text":"It must come from a deep desire to be\n\nSet free in My love, followed by a sincere\n\nUnyielding commitment to make your\n\nLove perfect through obedience..."},{"align":"center","text":"The shedding of the skin\n\nOf this world, the crucifying\n\nOf your old man with his sinful ways..."},{"align":"center","text":"The putting on of the new man\n\nWho is renewed in the knowledge\n\nOf The Holy One, conforming to the\n\nImage of Him who created him {{ref:Colossians 3:9-10}}..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"lead-by-example","num":51,"title":"Lead by Example","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Strive to walk as I walked, and they will see,\n\nFor every veil is lifted in Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Be steadfast and forthcoming;\n\nMake honesty your companion\n\nAnd integrity your close friend..."},{"align":"center","text":"Lead by example, with quiet boldness\n\nAnd steadfast trust, and they will begin to see..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"a-shining-example","num":52,"title":"A Shining Example","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"To abide in the doctrine of The Messiah\n\nIs not mere proclamation or belief..."},{"align":"center","text":"To abide in His doctrine is to LIVE by His words,\n\nA shining example of righteousness,\n\nStriving always to make your love\n\nPerfect through obedience..."},{"align":"center","text":"That those close to you, even to the passerby,\n\nMay see your good works and glorify\n\nYour Father in Heaven..."},{"align":"center","text":"_For it is written:\n\nOne does not live on bread and\n\nWater alone, but by every word that\n\nComes from the mouth of God {{ref:Matthew 4:4}}..._"},{"align":"center","text":"So then do not just give voice and preach,\n\nBut ABIDE in the doctrine of The Messiah..."},{"align":"center","text":"By example shall you lead them..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"let-the-law-be-written-in-your-heart","num":53,"title":"Let The Law Be Written in Your Heart","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I am the fulfillment of The Law,\n\nThe very goal at which the Torah aims..."},{"align":"center","text":"Thus all those who embrace Me\n\nAre freed from the curse of The Law,\n\nBut by no means are they now free\n\nTo forsake The Law..."},{"align":"center","text":"Rather let The Law be written in your heart..."},{"align":"center","text":"For now you are under grace,\n\nAnd by the power of My own spirit\n\nAre you now able to keep The Law..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"first-partakers","num":54,"title":"First Partakers","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"God is just in everything..."},{"align":"center","text":"And if The Father’s justice is not partial,\n\nThen it shall surely come to pass in these\n\nLatter days, that those who have\n\nPlaced themselves first shall be last..."},{"align":"center","text":"And those who were seen as last\n\nShall be first partakers of The Glory..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"be-born-again","num":55,"title":"Be Born Again","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Repent in sincerity and in truth..."},{"align":"center","text":"Return to your First Love,\n\nWalk in the first works;\n\nEmbrace The Word of God anew,\n\nBringing forth works worthy of repentance..."},{"align":"center","text":"That you may truly be born again..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"a-continual-washing","num":56,"title":"A Continual Washing","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"I tell you a mystery: It has been appointed to those who are born twice to die once, but by no means shall they die a second time. Yet those who do not come to Me in repentance shall be born once and die twice. Yet there are some among this generation who shall never taste death, having already passed from judgment into life.\n\nThus to My chosen elect, there is a death of the body unto resurrection. Yet for those still living at My return, there is a death of another kind - _the crucifying of your old man with his sinful ways, the putting on of the new man who is renewed in the knowledge of the Truth, restored in the image of Him who created him. {{ref:Colossians 3:9-10}}_\n\nThus when one is born into this world, the child and the mother suffer the pangs of childbirth, until the birth is complete. In the same way, those born of the Spirit shall suffer travail. For they are not yet separated from their flesh or this world, in which they continually stumble."},{"align":"center","text":"So then, being born again is the process\n\nBy which you are restored in the image of God,\n\nA continual washing, until you come into glory..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"reborn","num":57,"title":"Reborn","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"As a babe is born naked and wrapped in soft linens,\n\nSo also shall My people be reborn -\n\nNaked, void of the things of this world,\n\nClothed in fine linens of white..."},{"align":"center","text":"_Behold, the corruptible has put on incorruption,\n\nAnd the mortal, immortality, as it is written {{ref:1 Corinthians 15:54}}..._"},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-perfect-lamb","num":58,"title":"The Perfect Lamb","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I carried the weight of the world’s sin to the cross,\n\nAnd crucified sin through My suffering -\n\nThe penalty of sin abolished as I fell asleep,\n\nThe Victory established for all time upon My rising..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am and will always be The Perfect Lamb,\n\nWithout spot or blemish, given up for many..."},{"align":"center","text":"The Restoration of All Things..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"one-source","num":59,"title":"One Source","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"That which glorifies Me can have only one source..."},{"align":"center","text":"And that which denies My sacrifice, as though it\n\nWere not enough, steals from My glory,\n\nAnd this also has one source..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"i-shall-not-lose-one","num":60,"title":"I Shall Not Lose One","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I forgive all who return to Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Even the one in ninety-nine who goes astray;\n\nEven the one among twelve who betrays Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am The Lord..."},{"align":"center","text":"And of all those The Father\n\nHas given Me, I shall not lose one..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"fear-not","num":61,"title":"Fear Not","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved, I know when each will come to Me, I know every trial and tribulation. Therefore, call on My name in this time of darkness, in this time of great calamity and fear. Hold fast through all these tears, endure in these times of trouble."},{"align":"center","text":"Fear not, for I have overcome the world;\n\nI hold the keys of death and Sheol,\n\nAnd The Book of Life is held\n\nSecurely in My right hand..."},{"align":"center","text":"No one can steal you from My love;\n\nNo one can pluck you from My hand;\n\nNo one can break off what I have grafted in..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I know you as you are and as you will be,\n\nWith Me where I am..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"true-wisdom","num":62,"title":"True Wisdom","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"True wisdom is not of man, nor is it found in the earth, but from above - heavenly, holy. For that created was created according to the wisdom of Him who created it and by whom all things consist, knowing their form from the beginning.\n_Therefore the fear of The Lord is indeed the beginning of wisdom, and the knowledge of The Holy One is understanding, as it is written. {{ref:Proverbs 9:10}}_ For apart from Me there is no knowledge, apart from Me all understanding passes away. For I AM HE, The Only Fountain from which flows all wisdom and knowledge, The Source of all things."},{"align":"center","text":"So then all who receive of Me grow wise,\n\nReceiving of that which is pure,\n\nLearning to walk in that which is eternal..."},{"align":"center","text":"As one being led along a mountain stream\n\nOf living waters, filled with a fervent\n\nDesire to seek out its source..."},{"align":"center","text":"Drinking from it along the way,\n\nGaining strength in weakness,\n\nLeaving all behind in their holy pursuit..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-only-truth","num":63,"title":"The Only Truth","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I AM..."},{"align":"center","text":"And you are in life because of Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"And all that is, even all these worlds\n\nTo every star you see in the heavens,\n\nWas made according to the wisdom\n\nOf The Father, brought forth and established\n\nThrough The Son, by whom all things consist..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I AM, and have always been,\n\nThe Way and The Life, The Salvation of God,\n\nThe Only Truth from which all understanding flows..."},{"align":"center","text":"YAHUSHUA-YAHUWAH."}]},{"id":"faithful","num":64,"title":"Faithful","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"One who truly loves Me speaks about Me,\n\nAnd remains faithful at all times and in every season;\n\nAnd one who places Me above all else has shown their\n\nLoved ones who is first, and what faithfulness truly is..."},{"align":"center","text":"For there is no true love apart from Me;\n\nNor can one remain faithful unless\n\nThey have received of Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore to speak of Me in the\n\nCompany of others is to love them..."},{"align":"center","text":"And to deny Me in the company of others\n\nIs to hate them, whereby you have also\n\nRevealed that your comfort is of more\n\nImportance than The Truth, and keeping\n\nThe peace more important than their lives..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"patience-and-faith","num":65,"title":"Patience and Faith","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"What is the knowledge of man? Is it not a stone of stumbling? And the pride of man, a rock of offense? How then shall the blind see or the deaf hear, unless I heal them? Or how shall one grab hold of the line, unless it is first placed within their reach?"},{"align":"center","text":"Yet My servants are wise..."},{"align":"center","text":"They fear The Lord, and wait upon Me\n\nWith all patience and faith, doubting nothing,\n\nHumble servants who study My Word, knowing\n\nI am The Author and The Finisher thereof..."},{"align":"center","text":"When they wake and when they lie down, I am there..."},{"align":"center","text":"I am their life, and they are My joy..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"impasse","num":66,"title":"Impasse","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"When My servants come to an impasse in My Word, according to their own understanding, what is their reaction? They continue on, without hindrance or doubt.\n\nFor their relationship with The Author is intimate, their trust without reservation. Thus they remain at peace, and wait upon The Lord for the light of understanding, knowing in their heart every word is true, ready to receive the spirit of the Word, stumbling not over its letter.\n\nAnd until My people are established firmly upon this premise, they will remain daunted, striving to see but never fully understanding, straining to hear but remaining dull of hearing."},{"align":"center","text":"Thus for My wise and faithful servants,\n\nAll barriers are removed..."},{"align":"center","text":"For their peace is in the knowing,\n\nI AM WHO I AM, though they yet\n\nStand at the beginning, unable to see the end..."},{"align":"center","text":"An heir of all I will reveal to them\n\nWhen the fullness of time has come in..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"be-joined-unto-me","num":67,"title":"Be Joined Unto Me","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I have called My people out, that they might\n\nCome out from among them and be separate..."},{"align":"center","text":"A people set apart for My name,\n\nA people who keep The Commandments\n\nAnd cease not from testifying to My glory,\n\nA people of pure and undefiled faith..."},{"align":"center","text":"A people joined unto ME..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"the-watchmen","num":68,"title":"The Watchmen","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Consider the squirrel and its ways..."},{"align":"center","text":"Does it not live among the trees,\n\nRunning up and down with ease,\n\nLeaping from branch to branch with skill and grace,\n\nPerfectly designed for its abode and purpose?..."},{"align":"center","text":"So shall My watchmen be in the Day of The Lord..."},{"align":"center","text":"Prepared, according to their task;\n\nEstablished, according to the Word of My mouth;\n\nFilled, according to their service;\n\nRemade, according to My purpose..."},{"align":"center","text":"I AM THE LORD."}]},{"id":"a-wise-and-faithful-servant","num":69,"title":"A Wise and Faithful Servant","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Who is a wise and faithful servant?..."},{"align":"center","text":"Is he not one who receives the blessings\n\nOf his Father without constraint, one who\n\nEmbraces My speech, whether soft or hard,\n\nEven of that which I have spoken to another?..."},{"align":"center","text":"A servant such as this is wise indeed..."},{"align":"center","text":"_For he knows that every good gift\n\nAnd every perfect gift is from above,\n\nAnd comes down from The Father of Lights,\n\nWith whom there is no variation or\n\nShadow of turning, as it is written {{ref:James 1:17}}..._"},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"mindfulness","num":70,"title":"Mindfulness","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"What is a son who is mindful of his father’s ways, who pays close attention to his every word? Or a servant, who seeks only to serve his master? Or a faithful bride, who seeks always to please her husband in all her ways, whether he is near or far, in her presence or soon returning?"},{"align":"center","text":"Beloved ones, be mindful of\n\nThese things and grow in wisdom,\n\nAbide in trust and do not waver;\n\nBe at peace..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am indeed coming quickly,\n\nAnd My reward is with Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"fixed-upon-the-goal","num":71,"title":"Fixed Upon The Goal","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Those who I have called out of a place\n\nShall in no wise return to it,\n\nNor shall they look back..."},{"align":"center","text":"They shall continue on toward safety,\n\nWith their eyes fixed upon The Goal,\n\nWalking always in line with the Spirit..."},{"align":"center","text":"Praying without ceasing,\n\nGiving heed to My leading,\n\nListening for My voice..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"renewed","num":72,"title":"Renewed","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Only those who seek that which is first,\n\nWho fill themselves up with that which\n\nIs most needful, will finish the day\n\nWith strength enough to face tomorrow..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore seek Me out at every opportunity,\n\nWhether for a moment or for the hour,\n\nThat you may be renewed in My presence..."},{"align":"center","text":"Looking always to The Blessed Hope,\n\nHaving tasted of it while in waiting..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"history-has-an-end","num":73,"title":"History Has an End","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I AM COME..."},{"align":"center","text":"The One who was has come;\n\nThe One who is, is come;\n\nThe One who is to come is coming\n\nQuickly to fulfill and complete..."},{"align":"center","text":"HISTORY HAS AN END!..."},{"align":"center","text":"And His name is The Great I AM,\n\nThe Holy One of Israel!..."},{"align":"center","text":"YAHUSHUA-YAHUWAH!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Immanu El!"}]},{"id":"i-am-enough","num":74,"title":"I Am Enough","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Beloved ones, you worry, yet I AM HE;\n\nYou weep, yet I AM HE;\n\nYou stumble, yet I AM HE;\n\nYour hearts tear and break over\n\nAll these sorrows, yet I AM HE..."},{"align":"center","text":"You struggle and are in turmoil,\n\nYou feel lost, yet I AM HE;\n\nYou grasp at the wind and have\n\nNo understanding, yet I AM HE..."},{"align":"center","text":"You are persecuted by those\n\nYou love, yet I AM HE;\n\nThe world hates you, yet I AM HE;\n\nEverything you have is passing away, yet I AM HE;\n\nDeath comes to take you into darkness, yet I AM HE!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Do you not understand?! I AM ENOUGH!\n\nThe One who sees, The One who knows!\n\nNo matter the time or the season,\n\nIn every moment of your life, I AM HE!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"choose","num":75,"title":"Choose","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, it is time to choose,\n\nTo make your decision..."},{"align":"center","text":"It is time to bring your\n\nHeart forward, and be healed,\n\nTo make your repentance full..."},{"align":"center","text":"It is time to fall into Me unreservedly;\n\nOr to depart, and walk through dry places..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"gifts-of-the-spirit","num":76,"title":"Gifts of the Spirit","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I call My servants out from among them,\n\nI appoint every office, and I Myself\n\nNumber their steps before them..."},{"align":"center","text":"For My gifts are given through the Spirit,\n\nAnd must also be received in Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"They are in no wise open to claim,\n\nNor shall anyone on earth assign them..."},{"align":"center","text":"For only those in union with\n\nThe Messiah are able to walk in them..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"in-due-season","num":77,"title":"In Due Season","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"I have a great vineyard, with many grapes. I have provided both the early and latter rain and tended every vine, pruning them with sure hands and delicate fingers. Yet many wither, while others fail to produce, and still others are slow to ripen.\n\nI have waited patiently and tended My vineyard, doing all that was necessary to produce a fair crop, and now it is time for harvest. Yet I tell you plainly, it shall be a very lowly crop, a very small harvest, for few have ripened to maturity. Thus they must be left to ripen in their season."},{"align":"center","text":"And though the winds shall be harsh\n\nAnd the rains rare, behold, even all\n\nManner of plagues shall come,\n\nI must not gather them\n\nUntil their due season..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"lukewarm","num":78,"title":"Lukewarm","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"One who treads the path, going up\n\nAnd down, stepping on and off at\n\nTheir convenience, treads not the path,\n\nBut is like one who treads water..."},{"align":"center","text":"By no means shall they be able\n\nTo keep their head above water,\n\nNor shall their strength deliver\n\nThem in the Day of Troubles..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"revived","num":79,"title":"Revived","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Behold, the day and hour is close at hand,\n\nYea it is very near, when the dead in Messiah\n\nShall arise and the sleepers shall awake,\n\nWhen the rotting corpses are revived\n\nAnd the dust gathers together once again..."},{"align":"center","text":"From one end of the earth to the other,\n\nEven from the deepest depths, shall My\n\nPeople rise up and give Me glory..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore let the children of Israel prepare,\n\nLet everyone joined to Messiah step forward\n\nAnd claim their inheritance..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I have but to call out your name..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Holy One of Israel."}]},{"id":"the-gathering-up","num":80,"title":"The Gathering Up","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Behold, the Glory of God breaks through\n\nThe clouds, a mighty trumpet blast\n\nSounds in all the earth!..."},{"align":"center","text":"From the heights of the mountains\n\nTo the deepest depths, life bursts forth\n\nIn the bodies of the dead!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, a loud voice is heard from Heaven:\n\n_“EARTH, GIVE UP YOUR DEAD!_\n\n_BRIDE OF THE BLESSED,_\n\n_COME UP HERE!”..._"},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"in-the-arms-of-the-king","num":81,"title":"In the Arms of The King","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"There is a place..."},{"align":"justify","text":"A place beyond space and time, where eternity dwells and life has no end, where light takes its form and goodness is revealed, where the eyes of the redeemed may look upon the Glory of God and see His face, where Heaven meets the earth and The Eternal dwells with men...\n\nA place where Everlasting Love can be embraced and healing flows like a gentle stream, a place where time has no meaning and the stars flee away, where the brightness is excellent and the warmth thereof very soothing...\n\nA place where joy comes by knowledge with pure understanding, where fulfillment comes by a strong embrace, and love’s completion is met with great satisfaction through many tears flowing down the cheeks of the forever young; a place where understanding bursts forth in realization, revelation beyond words!..."},{"align":"center","text":"A place where the hearts of the chosen are revealed,\n\nBehold, they are uncovered, revealing their true form;\n\nThe image in which I created them, restored..."},{"align":"center","text":"A simple quiet place, set apart..."},{"align":"center","text":"In the arms of The King."}]},{"id":"the-creator","num":82,"title":"The Creator","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"When I consider, all creation is before Me;\n\nFrom the most minute detail to the greatest,\n\nNothing is hidden from My eyes..."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, the whole universe abides\n\nWithin My understanding..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am LORD and GOD,\n\nCreator of Heaven and Earth."}]},{"id":"the-true-bride","num":83,"title":"The True Bride","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The Bride is chosen..."},{"align":"center","text":"My blood runs through her veins,\n\nMy image is shown upon her face..."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, the light of My coming is reflected\n\nIn her eyes, for I have captured her gaze,\n\nAnd she will by no means look away\n\nOr seek after another..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"heed-my-words","num":84,"title":"Heed My Words","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved ones, wait upon Me, with all trust and fear; stand steadfast and be patient. Accept My words, as I have spoken them and as they are written. Do not add to My words, nor take from them; neither form for yourselves any private interpretation. Only give heed to My words and also do them, and prepare."},{"align":"center","text":"For My words are indeed that light which\n\nShines in a dark place, a lamp and a beacon,\n\nPreparing My way before Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Until the new day dawns and\n\nThe Morning Star rises, filling the hearts\n\nOf My chosen as they enter in..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"followers-of-the-way","num":85,"title":"Followers of The Way","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"When those who call of\n\nThemselves Christian, ask you,\n\n_“To which church do you belong?”..._"},{"align":"center","text":"You shall answer them:\n\n_“I belong to no church named of men._\n\n_I belong to The Lord, YahuShua HaMashiach,_\n\n_Whom you call Jesus and Christ._\n\n_And together with all those who_\n\n_Remain in His love {{ref:John 15:10}} and obey His voice {{ref:John 3:36}}_\n\n_Is The Church in which I dwell”..._"},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"true-baptism","num":86,"title":"True Baptism","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Let My beloved first be baptized\n\nIn spirit and in truth, filled\n\nWith the knowledge of The Holy,\n\nNourished by the Word of Truth..."},{"align":"center","text":"Let them come to Me in sincere\n\nRepentance, and receive forgiveness\n\nOf sins in The Messiah’s name..."},{"align":"center","text":"All burdens lifted, immersed\n\nAnd purified in the Spirit of God..."},{"align":"center","text":"For The Holy One of Israel is\n\nHe who baptizes with the Holy Spirit\n\nAnd with fire, and He knows His own..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-beginning-of-wisdom","num":87,"title":"The Beginning of Wisdom","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Come together and reason, O sons of men. Look upon the works of My hands, and see with new eyes and restored vision, that you may behold the Truth.\n\nFor all the works of man are here for but a moment, then quickly pass away. And that which remains, shall it not become fuel for the fire in the Day of The Lord’s Anger? And the knowledge of man, is it not foolishness in My eyes, coming to nothing before the light of My Glory?"},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore fear The Lord your God,\n\nAnd accept the truth of who I am..."},{"align":"center","text":"_For the fear of The Lord is the beginning_\n\n_Of wisdom, and the knowledge_\n\n_Of The Holy One is understanding {{ref:Proverbs 9:10}}..._"},{"align":"center","text":"For I am God alone."}]},{"id":"remember-the-sabbath","num":88,"title":"Remember the Sabbath","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Those who remember the Sabbath honor Me, and those who rest on the Sabbath rest in Me, as they look to the Day. For I had set the seventh day apart, and sanctified it, from the beginning. {{ref:Genesis 2:3}} Thus it has been a sign between Me and My people, even to this day, and so shall it remain forever.\n\nFor as I spoke to the children of Israel, saying, _“Surely My Sabbaths you shall keep, for it is a sign between Me and you throughout your generations, that you may know that I am The Lord who sanctifies you,”{{ref:Exodus 31:13}}_ so also do I speak to you, even to all who are grafted in."},{"align":"center","text":"For those who obey My Commandments\n\nRemain in My love {{ref:John 15:10}}, and those who remember\n\nMy Sabbaths keep My company,\n\nFor The Holy One of Israel\n\nDwells in the midst of them..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I long for My children to be with Me\n\nWhere I am, I am eager to return them\n\nTo the Garden, that we may once again\n\nWalk together in the cool of the day."},{"align":"justify","text":"Therefore remember the Sabbath, and I shall remember you. Bless the Sabbath, and I shall bless you. Love one another, as I have loved you.\n\nPut away your works, look not to the cares of this world, and let go of your worries on the Sabbath day; spare yourselves the weight of all these troubles for just one day."},{"align":"center","text":"Let all your thoughts dwell upon\n\nYour God and Savior, and consider;\n\nYea, let your mind be filled with wonder\n\nAnd awe over the works of My hands..."},{"align":"center","text":"For even The Lord your God,\n\nCreator of Heaven and Earth,\n\nRested on the seventh day {{ref:Genesis 2:3}}..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"prepare-and-watch","num":89,"title":"Prepare and Watch","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"I am indeed coming down to shake the heavens and the earth, to move all from its place; to bring forth that which was hidden and to reveal that which was misplaced; to open that which was shut and to shut that which was opened.\n\nTherefore prepare, My people, for the time has come; yes, today is the day of salvation! Go forth, beloved ones, and set all these crooked paths straight; regain the line, prepare and watch. For the leaves of the fig tree are upon its branches; summer is near! {{ref:Matthew 24:32-34}}"},{"align":"center","text":"Again I say, watch!..."},{"align":"center","text":"For The One who ascended\n\nIs about to descend..."},{"align":"center","text":"_And lo, I am come, in the Volume_\n\n_Of the Book it is written of Me,_\n\n_To accomplish The Father’s will {{ref:Psalm 40:7-8}} · {{ref:Hebrews 10:7}}..._"},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-first-harvest","num":90,"title":"The First Harvest","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"It is written, _all shall lie down in death {{ref:Ecclesiastes 9:2-3}}..._\n\n\n\nYet there is a people who shall not sleep,\n\nNor shall they lie down in death -\nA people who shall be awake at My coming,\n\nA people who have received of the divine gift,\n\nA people who know Me and in whom I am known,\n\nFor I see of Myself within them."},{"align":"center","text":"They shall be lifted up, not preceding\n\nThose who have fallen asleep in Messiah;\n\nThis is the first harvest and resurrection."},{"align":"center","text":"For there is but One Way, One Truth, and One Life;\n\nFrom the beginning, there is but One..."},{"align":"center","text":"I AM HE..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"to-all-those-who-call-of-themselves-christian","num":91,"title":"To All Those Who Call of Themselves Christian","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Listen closely\n\nAnd take My words to heart,\n\nAll you who call of yourselves Christian:\n\nI ask you, do you really love Me?..."},{"align":"center","text":"Then follow Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Beloved ones, listen closely\n\nAnd take My words to heart,\n\nAll you who call of yourselves Christian:\n\nDo you really love Me?..."},{"align":"center","text":"Then obey My Word! Follow Me!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, listen closely\n\nAnd take My words to heart,\n\nAll you who call of yourselves Christian:\n\nDo you really love Me?!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Then heed My voice and come out!\n\nFOLLOW ME!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"bear-fruit","num":92,"title":"Bear Fruit","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved, bear fruit after the kind I have given you, in open and in secret. For what profit is there in sharing with another that which they believe they already have? And how shall one who pushes out the hand receive a gift?"},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, turn aside from those who\n\nPush out the hand and wag the head..."},{"align":"center","text":"Rather seek out the poor, that I may feed them..."},{"align":"center","text":"Fill the bowls of the hungry, and place\n\nThe cup in the hands of the thirsty;\n\nGive them your portion..."},{"align":"center","text":"For My bounty is plentiful,\n\nGiven freely to all who hunger\n\nAnd thirst for righteousness..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-spirit-of-god","num":93,"title":"The Spirit of God","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved ones, pray to your Father in Heaven, in The Son’s name, and through the Spirit we shall be one. For all My servants move, speak and hear Me through My spirit, and only through The Son shall My children come to know Me as I truly am... _And oh how blessed are those who know Him, for they love Him and obey His voice, having truly received of Him, even of His spirit, the Spirit of God._"},{"align":"center","text":"Indeed holy, holy, holy\n\nIs The Lord God Almighty..."},{"align":"center","text":"One God, invisible and visible,\n\nThe Father and The Son;\n\nAnd the Spirit called Holy,\n\nBecause I am holy..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"it-is-time","num":94,"title":"It Is Time","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Behold, the time has come for My name to resound in all the earth, for all who dwell upon the earth to be humbled, to be broken without hand. Indeed, now is the time for all who have ears to hear, to hear and give heed; and for those who refuse, to forbear and rebel against Me."},{"align":"center","text":"It is time for My servants to stand up,\n\nTo receive My words and also do them;\n\nIt is time to blow the trumpet, to sound the alarm..."},{"align":"center","text":"It is time for My spirit to be poured out,\n\nFor the hand of The Almighty to stir up\n\nThe multitudes, for The Word of God\n\nTo separate and divide the people..."},{"align":"center","text":"It is time for My watchmen to proclaim\n\nThe acceptable year of The Lord and the\n\nDay of Vengeance of The Lord their God..."},{"align":"center","text":"For the ears of the first election are open,\n\nAnd within My prophets I have placed\n\nMy voice, once again; I have surely\n\nPut My words in their mouths..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am The Lord, and I do not change."}]},{"id":"the-spirit-of-the-word","num":95,"title":"The Spirit of the Word","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Do not judge according to human standards, nor by that which is put forth by men as doctrine, for they are greatly misled. _Rather study to show yourself approved unto God, a workman that need not be ashamed, rightly dividing the Word of Truth. {{ref:2 Timothy 2:15}}_ For discernment with fear is righteousness."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, beloved, remember:\n\nThe spirit of the Word, and not the letter,\n\nIs the way, the truth and the life..."},{"align":"center","text":"For The Messiah is indeed coming quickly,\n\nTo baptize all in fire and glory..."},{"align":"center","text":"Those of a wicked heart, in fire..."},{"align":"center","text":"And those of the Spirit,\n\nIn glory, forever and ever!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"inheritance","num":96,"title":"Inheritance","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Behold, My people are afflicted,\n\nAnd My faithful ones are persecuted,\n\nImprisoned and put to death!\n\nMy little ones are brought to harm,\n\nAnd the innocent are murdered in droves,\n\nCAST OFF AS REFUSE!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore the afflicted shall be\n\nGiven wealth beyond imagining,\n\nAnd the meek shall inherit the earth;\n\nThe little ones shall be taken,\n\nAnd the innocent shall return home..."},{"align":"center","text":"And they shall be My sons and daughters,\n\nForever, life without end..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"restoration","num":97,"title":"Restoration","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I AM THE RESURRECTION AND THE LIFE!..."},{"align":"center","text":"And all who believe in Me shall not die, but live,\n\nFor I shall raise them up at the Last Day!..."},{"align":"center","text":"No more tears, no more death, no more pain,\n\nFor the old order of things has passed away;\n\nAll things restored in glory, the glory of everlasting life!..."},{"align":"center","text":"I AM RISEN! YOUR REDEEMER LIVES!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Holy One of Israel."}]},{"id":"call-upon-the-name","num":98,"title":"Call Upon The Name","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"The wicked shall surely fall by the word of their own mouth, and by their works shall they stumble into the pit; behold, by their every word and deed have they condemned themselves to death."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet if these same ones turn from their\n\nIniquity, and call upon Me in the name\n\nOf The Messiah, they shall live and not die;\n\nThey shall surely be delivered!..."},{"align":"center","text":"For they have called upon The Name,\n\nThe only name under Heaven\n\nBy which you must be saved..."},{"align":"center","text":"For He is called Jesus and Christ..."},{"align":"center","text":"His name: YAHUSHUA HAMASHIACH,\n\nBoth Lord and Savior of men..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says YAHUWAH."}]},{"id":"all-shall-be-fulfilled","num":99,"title":"All Shall Be Fulfilled","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"As I have commanded it, so shall it be done. As I have spoken it, so shall it come to pass. As I have purposed it, so shall it be accomplished. For My glory, all shall be fulfilled.\n\nThus that which I have spoken by My prophets shall surely be. And though they stumble, they shall by no means fall, for they do continually humble themselves before Me."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, blessed is the man who comes\n\nTo Me ashamed of his trespasses, whose heart\n\nIs full of grief on account of his sins,\n\nFor I am faithful to forgive his sins..."},{"align":"center","text":"Indeed I shall lift him up,\n\nAnd set his feet upon hallowed ground..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"daily-bread","num":100,"title":"Daily Bread","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Understand the Word of My mouth and that which is set before you, even upon each of your plates: I have bore you, even twice have you come forth - First by water and blood in the flesh, and a second time in the Spirit, yea even a third time when you shall come into glory.\n\nAnd behold, that which is first sown in your hearts is The Living Word. And that which grows from Me bears fruit, according to the food and drink I provide, the written Word. Therefore both are necessary, yet one must be first."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet understand this:\n\nOne who is awakened can not remain so,\n\nUnless they receive of Me and also\n\nEat of that which I provide..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore abide in Me,\n\nAnd partake daily of My supper..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"true-knowledge","num":101,"title":"True Knowledge","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Who among you has committed no murder, whether in heart or in action? Who among you has committed no adultery, whether in heart or in action? Who among you, O peoples of the earth, has committed no sin?!\n\nBehold, all have fallen short of the Glory of God, all have failed utterly in their attempts to gain righteousness; even the works of the most righteous among you are but filthy rags before Me. And for this reason did I come into the world, manifest in the flesh, to bear the full weight of the sin of this world - Immanu El."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore get wisdom, get understanding,\n\nAnd seek My face in sincerity and in truth..."},{"align":"center","text":"Humble yourselves,\n\nThat you may receive true knowledge,\n\nThat you may come to know Me as I truly am..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"one-fold","num":102,"title":"One Fold","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Where does a shepherd spend his time, and which of his sheep require the most attention? Therefore pray in like manner. For indeed the ill of the flock require the most attention, and the one in ninety-nine who has gone astray shall by no means be forsaken.\n\nAnd though there are many who stand inside locked gates, while you stand outside, do you not remain all of one fold? And when I have freed them, will you not all rejoice together? Therefore treat them as such, and pray for them, even double, and it shall be well with you. For those who arrive last shall be embraced by those who had arrived first."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore let your heart remember,\n\nAs you look to the day..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"mercy","num":103,"title":"Mercy","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Hear and understand the loving mercies of God fulfilled in Me, even of those bitter tears which I have shed over all these who deny Me, over all these who betray Me by all they say and do: Beloved, in My anger I have indeed cast them out, appointing others to run in their stead. Yet I tell you the truth, though they now abide as one sitting along the wayside, they are in no wise broken off. For our bond is love, and any bond forged in My love can never be broken."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, even amongst My flock\n\nHave I received many kisses\n\nAfter the kind of My son, Judas..."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet I tell you the truth, I have\n\nNever lost one who is Mine;\n\nI am in love with My own..."},{"align":"center","text":"And though their thoughts betray\n\nThem, having given heed to many lies\n\nAnd deceptions from within and without,\n\nI know My own, and I will never turn\n\nAway anyone who returns to Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"peace","num":104,"title":"Peace","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"My sons and daughters, from the beginning, I AM WHO I AM and shall be. Even to the end, I AM HE. From everlasting to everlasting, I AM. In this shall you find rest and know peace, says The Lord.\n\nTherefore no longer bind yourselves to what you see, nor concern yourselves with the things of this world and its evil ways. Free yourselves by the knowledge I have given you, by the understanding that I AM WHO I AM, freedom in the knowing I AM HE."},{"align":"center","text":"Beloved ones, I have defeated the world,\n\nI have overcome your sins;\n\nDeath is put to death because of Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, I am risen, death is turned backward..."},{"align":"center","text":"Only life is and shall be..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"refuge","num":105,"title":"Refuge","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, there is but One Refuge,\n\nOnly One Way to be found..."},{"align":"center","text":"In Mashiach ONLY shall you find\n\nRefuge from all these troubles;\n\nThrough Him ONLY have I opened The Way..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, My people, call upon the name\n\nOf The Lord in your darkest hour!..."},{"align":"center","text":"For it is time for the name of mercy\n\nAnd pure righteousness to be glorified!\n\nIt is time for God’s Salvation to be revealed\n\nTo the first election, for the supplications\n\nOf His people to be fulfilled to the fullest!..."},{"align":"center","text":"LET THEM BE DELIVERED!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-power-of-my-love","num":106,"title":"The Power of My Love","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"How long shall the multitudes swear by things made, and place their trust in the works of man?! For the desolate know not the things of God, nor is darkness able to understand; yea, the wicked gnash upon their teeth, the whole body convulses in the wake of mourning, for there is no rest."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet My hand caresses the cheeks of the hopeless,\n\nAs we watch the dawning of the day together..."},{"align":"center","text":"For the strength of My arm uplifts the downtrodden,\n\nMy strong embrace heals the sorrowful,\n\nEvery beat of My heart revives the dead,\n\nAnd the sound of My voice frees every captive..."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, the power of My love hides them away!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-will-of-god","num":107,"title":"The Will of God","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Nothing, nothing in all creation,\n\nCan usurp the will of The Most High God!\n\nNor shall any run out ahead of Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"MY will shall be done on earth as it is in Heaven..."},{"align":"center","text":"For it is purposed and can not be moved,\n\nHaving been written in everlasting stone\n\nFrom the very foundation of the world..."},{"align":"center","text":"I AM THE LORD."}]},{"id":"made-for-the-son","num":108,"title":"Made For The Son","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"You are and were created in fragile flesh,\n\nBeautifully crafted by the hand of your Father,\n\nHaving been made alive in The Son..."},{"align":"center","text":"In His image you are and were created,\n\nIn love I created you, placing you\n\nIn the garden to My own joy..."},{"align":"center","text":"My own beloved who have received of My breath..."},{"align":"center","text":"Created by The Father, made for The Son..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"across-all-boundaries","num":109,"title":"Across All Boundaries","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"That atoned for by My blood\n\nIs far-reaching, even across all boundaries,\n\nLife and death, time and space..."},{"align":"center","text":"For even those before Me were after Me,\n\nAnd knew The Father, who knowing Him\n\nKnew and saw the time of My coming,\n\nHaving repented before The Father\n\nIn His name, which is also My name,\n\nThe name We shared before the world was made..."},{"align":"center","text":"Thus by the heart is one judged,\n\nOf which I know, for nothing is hidden before Me;\n\nI made you and know you, having always known you;\n\nEven those who will yet come to Me, I see and know..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I see you as you are and will be,\n\nWith Me where I am..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"the-way-is-provided","num":110,"title":"The Way Is Provided","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Come now and share in My joy,\n\nAbide in My love, enter into My rest..."},{"align":"center","text":"For The Way is provided, The Lamb sacrificed,\n\nMy own beating heart stilled in death,\n\nMy own blood poured out\n\nSo you may return to Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"The curtain is torn; the way is open!\n\nApproach and draw near to Me; hear Me calling!..."},{"align":"center","text":"For The Ladder of Heaven is joined to earth,\n\nGlorified and named above all names!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-tame-of-my-flock","num":111,"title":"The Tame of My Flock","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"All who truly receive of Me know Me, and I live in them. And if I live in them, then in no wise will these turn away. For one who abides in My love shall never leave it.\n\nFor they have tasted of the divine gift and have looked upon My glory. They will not depart from Me, but rest securely at My right hand. These are My sheep, the tame of My flock. They call out and I do hear them, even as I had called to them and they did hear."},{"align":"center","text":"All My sheep hear My voice\n\nAnd know the sound of My voice,\n\nAnd seek to follow Me wheresoever I lead them..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"for-my-own-name-s-sake","num":112,"title":"For My Own Name’s Sake","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Behold, My own people go the way\n\nOf the ungodly, following after those void\n\nOf the Spirit, married to this world!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet I shall save them out of all their troubles;\n\nFor My own name’s sake will I do it..."},{"align":"center","text":"For the sake of Judah, I shall cover them;\n\nFor the sake of Jacob, I shall hold them in safety;\n\nAnd for the sake of David, My servant, I shall\n\nShelter them under the shadow of My wings..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"keeping-the-law","num":113,"title":"Keeping The Law","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Say no more, _“Grace versus The Law.”_\n\nSay rather, _“Grace AND The Law”_..."},{"align":"center","text":"For Grace is the fulfillment of The Law;\n\nAnd where there is an absence of grace,\n\nThere is lawlessness..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, keeping The Law\n\nIs a reflection of My own spirit in you..."},{"align":"center","text":"And oh how blessed are those who have\n\nReceived of Grace, and seek to please The Father\n\nBy obeying His Law, and teach men so..."},{"align":"center","text":"Grace AND The Law..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"nothing-is-hidden-before-me","num":114,"title":"Nothing Is Hidden Before Me","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Nothing exists outside of Me, says The Lord; neither does anything continue outside My will. For even the evil of this present world is set within the confines of My will. For evil acts and brings forth of its own, yet is unaware that nothing is hidden before Me; neither has anything come to pass, nor will be, that I have not already beheld. And this, O arrogant and deceived generation, is why I said, _“All was written and completed, even before the foundation of the world.”_"},{"align":"center","text":"For I am God, THE GOD!\n\nThe God of Abraham, The God of Isaac,\nThe God of Jacob, The God of all!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Even of all that is known and unknown,\n\nThe Creator of all things..."},{"align":"center","text":"The Everlasting, who is from\n\nEverlasting to everlasting..."},{"align":"center","text":"I AM."}]},{"id":"not-by-human-means","num":115,"title":"Not By Human Means","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"What I have prepared can not be seen\n\nWith the eyes, nor can it be attained\n\nBy human means or mere proclamation..."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet within the hearts of My own\n\nIt is clearly seen, and upon the lips\n\nOf My bride the testimony is clearly heard..."},{"align":"center","text":"For that which has entered into the hearts\n\nOf the chosen shall soon be realized,\n\nAnd that which has entered into the hearts\n\nOf the wicked shall return upon their own heads..."},{"align":"center","text":"For hate brings forth suffering and violence..."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet the love of The Messiah brings salvation,\n\nEscape under the shadow of His healing wings!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"according-to-the-number","num":116,"title":"According to the Number","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I am The Lord..."},{"align":"center","text":"And though I bruise, I will surely heal;\n\nAnd though I pour out strong judgment,\n\nI will also show mercy..."},{"align":"center","text":"For all appointed to captivity shall go into captivity,\n\nYet I will deliver them, even all who call on the\n\nName of The Lord in that day..."},{"align":"center","text":"And though many will be brought low,\n\nEven down to the depths of darkness and despair,\n\nBehold, from the depths I shall raise\n\nThem up, even high above the heavens;\n\nEven from the ashes shall I bring them forth,\n\nAnd they shall give Me perfect praise in the\n\nTabernacle of My glory!..."},{"align":"center","text":"And so it is fulfilled, and shall also come to pass:\n\nThe first shall be last, and the last\n\nShall be first partakers of the glory;\n\nYet all will be saved according\n\nTo the number The Lord shall call..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-bride","num":117,"title":"The Bride","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The true bride is chosen;\n\nShe has been called out and shall be lifted up!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, I will come for her and she will be taken,\n\nCaught up to My Father’s house for one week\n\nIn The Lord, and we shall be together forever..."},{"align":"center","text":"All tears wiped away..."},{"align":"center","text":"Even every tear she shed on the behalf of others;\n\nEvery tear she shed for the afflicted and the unborn;\n\nEvery tear she shed over all this evil,\n\nOn account of all this oppression and death..."},{"align":"center","text":"Even every tear she shed in repentance,\n\nIn seeking after her Bridegroom..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"reverence","num":118,"title":"Reverence","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Peoples of the earth, do you know Me? Do you really know who I am? I am Elohim. YAHUSHUA-YAHUWAH is My name, both God and Savior. For in The Son does the fullness of The Father dwell..."},{"align":"justify","text":"Yet I ask you, who among the nations fears Me? Who among this modern generation, among all these multitudes of perverse and vile people, revere My name? Who, among this great multitude, trembles in fear at the coming of The Lord?! And who among the mighty shall be able to stand, when the wrath of God is revealed from Heaven?!"},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore repent, and establish My way before Me,\n\nSays The Lord God, and I shall also establish you..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am The Lord, and I shall\n\nEstablish justice in all the earth."}]},{"id":"indwelt","num":119,"title":"Indwelt","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Who has given heed to the voice\n\nOf The Lord their God?\n\nWho has come out to meet Me?..."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, the lowly have come out,\n\nThe poor in spirit have come forth,\n\nThe broken have sought Me and\n\nThe faithful uphold My cause..."},{"align":"center","text":"Yes, these who carry The Messiah\n\nWithin them have come forward to\n\nPartake of My supper, and do follow\n\nThe Lamb wheresoever He leads them..."},{"align":"center","text":"And behold, the day is near when He shall\n\nCall out to His beloved, and all those who\n\nHave ears to hear will be lifted up;\n\nThey shall surely be gone from this place!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"blessed-be-the-name","num":120,"title":"Blessed Be The Name","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Behold, My name alone stands throughout\n\nThe generations, a perpetual covering for My people,\n\nA secure place of shelter for all those who seek My face,\n\nA tower of strength for all who take refuge in Me...\n\n\n\nFrom everlasting, I AM, and to everlasting shall I be,\n\nThe same and unchanging, even as My name..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I AM WHO I AM..."},{"align":"center","text":"YAHUWAH, The One who causes to be;\n\nYAHUSHUA, He by whom all things\n\nConsist and have life..."},{"align":"center","text":"Thus My name is one, even as\n\nThe Father and The Son are one,\n\nA just God and a Savior - ONE..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-holy-days","num":121,"title":"The Holy Days","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The significance of The Holy Days is found\n\nIn their meaning and revealed by their order..."},{"align":"center","text":"Even as all find their fulfillment in The Messiah\n\nAnd their completion in the coming of The Lord..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"set-apart","num":122,"title":"Set Apart","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, stand apart from\n\nThis world in word and by deed;\n\nTake your every thought captive\n\nThat you may be fully set apart..."},{"align":"center","text":"Reveal your love for Me by all you say\n\nAnd do; put your love on open display!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Rest in Me on the Sabbath Day\n\nAnd receive My blessing;\n\nHonor My Holy Days and remember,\n\nThat you may also understand;\n\nHold fast to The Holy Covenant,\n\nAnd no longer depart from\n\nThe Word of My Commandment..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"beloved-awake","num":123,"title":"Beloved, Awake","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, awake! Awake from your slumber!\n\nAwaken your hearts to The Majesty on High!\n\nEmbrace the full revelation of\n\nWHO I AM, of all I have done!..."},{"align":"center","text":"For the Word of The Lord\n\nFlows like water, My love runs pure..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore embrace My words and receive\n\nOf My love, that you may be filled with My spirit,\n\nTo the bearing of much fruit in The Beloved..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"penitent","num":124,"title":"Penitent","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"It is the penitent man who shall know God,\n\nAnd penitent you must be; die to yourselves daily..."},{"align":"center","text":"Cast off the skin of this world and walk with\n\nMe as I am, and not as you would have Me be..."},{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, cast off your sins, depart quickly from\n\nTemptation, and to the accuser turn a deaf ear;\n\nFor I tell you the truth, evil has lost\n\nIts grip on the redeemed..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore hear My words, and also do them;\n\nGive heed to My speech, and embrace\n\nAll I have given you..."},{"align":"center","text":"Drink deeply from this cup,\n\nAnd be created anew..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord your Redeemer."}]},{"id":"the-god-of-justice","num":125,"title":"The God of Justice","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I am The Lord..."},{"align":"center","text":"I know what is most needful,\n\nI alone do what is right..."},{"align":"center","text":"And though I afflict, I will also heal;\n\nAnd though I strike the people in My wrath,\n\nI will also bind up their wounds..."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, I shall bring the kingdoms\n\nOf men to utter ruin, and make\n\nThe face of the earth a desolation;\n\nFor I AM HE who shall create new heavens\n\nAnd a new earth, in which justice shall\n\nRun down like water and righteousness\n\nLike an ever-flowing stream..."},{"align":"center","text":"For as I have spoken, so I speak;\n\nAs I am, so shall I be..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The King of Power and Glory,\n\nThe Only Lord of Hosts, The Holy One of Israel."}]},{"id":"spare-the-rod","num":126,"title":"Spare the Rod","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"You have heard it said, to spare the rod is to hate your child. This Scripture is true. Yet I tell you the truth, the rod is discipline, and not that of physical punishment.\n\nO vain and ignorant people, stop perverting the Scriptures of Truth! Humble yourselves, that you may gain wisdom. A child’s disobedience is brought forth from a troubled heart and an unsettled spirit, wrought in ignorance. How then shall a beating correct the heart, or striking them with a rod bring about a right spirit?"},{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, do not exasperate your children\n\nBy bringing them into subjection by abuse..."},{"align":"center","text":"Rather take them by the hand, and lead\n\nThem in the ways of The Lord, with love..."},{"align":"center","text":"For the love of a father is displayed in\n\nTenderness and kindness, and is also\n\nRevealed through the correction and\n\nDiscipline of those he loves..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-seed-and-the-sower","num":127,"title":"The Seed and The Sower","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved, you must ask yourselves, “Where have all these seeds been sown? Have they taken root? Or are they choked by the multitude of weeds which have sprung up?” Beware, for the birds gather, and wait eagerly to devour all seeds which have fallen by the wayside."},{"align":"center","text":"Thus only that which is first shall bear fruit;\n\nFor that which is foremost bears fruit\n\nAccording to the Seed and\n\nThe One who has sown it..."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet that which is put first by men, which is\n\nNot of the Seed nor of The Sower, must die;\n\nIt must be uprooted and cast into the fire..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"true-forgiveness","num":128,"title":"True Forgiveness","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Begin again in Me, says The Lord, for I have not left you. Behold, I am with you, even to the end of this age."},{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved, you are forgiven. And in true forgiveness, there is no remembrance of past offenses; behold, even your sins of tomorrow are washed away. Therefore fix your gaze upon Me, focus not on your sin; give temptation no power, and to the accuser turn a deaf ear."},{"align":"center","text":"Indeed, come all who struggle and are\n\nHeavy-laden, and I will give you rest..."},{"align":"center","text":"Take My yoke upon you and learn from Me,\n\nFor I am gentle and lowly in heart,\n\nAnd in Me you will find rest for your souls..."},{"align":"center","text":"For My yoke is easy, and My burden light, {{ref:Matthew 11:28-30}}\n\nFor all those who trust in Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-fear-of-the-lord","num":129,"title":"The Fear of The Lord","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"It is written: _The fear of The Lord is the beginning of wisdom, and knowledge of The Holy One is understanding. {{ref:Proverbs 9:10}}_\n\nTherefore all else is vanity, a false way, leading to great vexation of spirit. For I AM THE LORD. From the beginning it was I who had done it; even to the end shall I perform it; and behold, all is fulfilled according to My will."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore to fear The Lord your God\n\nIs indeed the beginning of wisdom..."},{"align":"center","text":"For how can one know Me,\n\nUnless they first acknowledge Me?\n\nAnd how can one fear Me, unless they\n\nBelieve, I AM WHO I AM?..."},{"align":"center","text":"He who causes to be,\n\nHe who called all things into existence,\n\nThe Creator of Heaven and Earth..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-living-bread","num":130,"title":"The Living Bread","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Have I not provided a bounty? Have I not poured out and sent forth the call? Therefore let those who have come out abide in Me until the time, and eat also of this bread. For I shall be with them, yes, even I Myself shall be with them, close at hand, and they shall fellowship with Me in the secret place. They have all they need.\n\nYet let those who reject Me and My Word, even this blessing which I have given to this generation, walk through dry places. For I have left them desolate. And so they must walk, they must tread the path they have chosen, until the time be changed, until they are broken without hand. I AM THE LORD."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, again I say,\n\nTo all those who have ears to hear:\n\nSeek not the table, but He who sits at it..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"walk-in-me","num":131,"title":"Walk In Me","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"There are none like Me, beloved, nor has there ever been one whose love surpasses understanding, a love without end. For I had paid the ransom from the beginning, a dowry the likes of which has never been seen, a bride-price from The God of Heaven.\n\nBeloved, I stretched out My hands for you; I bore the weight of your sins, I carried your burdens! Therefore is My grace sufficient for you. Yet you must choose to stand up and walk in Me, relying on My strength in your times of weakness, by which My strength and your trust is made perfect.\n\nHave I not said, _“In obedience is your love made perfect,”_ and, _“Who you choose, not what you choose, is the answer”?_ And when you have chosen Me, is it not also your reasonable service to walk in Me?"},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, again I say, choose..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am The Only Way,\n\nThe Only Truth, The Only Life..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"service-and-sacrifice","num":132,"title":"Service and Sacrifice","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"I tell you the truth, ALL who forsake the poor and the needy, and the fatherless and the widow, do not know Me, and have no place with Me at My supper, until they become as those they have forsaken. For by no other means will they learn true compassion."},{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, to drink My blood is\n\nTo receive of Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"To give up everything is to walk in Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"To suffer is to know Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"And to die for another is to know\n\nThe depths of My love."},{"align":"justify","text":"Yet I do not ask you to die for another, only that you push through - that you shatter all this stained glass with which you surround yourselves; that you be broken in pieces and truly become My disciples; that you love one another, even all those I send to you; that you surrender your lives and be created anew, trusting in Me to supply all that is needful... _Trust which comes by service and sacrifice, says The Lord._"}]},{"id":"according-to-my-will-and-purpose","num":133,"title":"According to My Will and Purpose","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved ones, all My sheep hear My voice. Yet each receives in proportion to their faith and in accordance with My will and purpose. For a willing, humble heart is open to Me, and one who is deeply in love with Me will hear My voice. Yet this is not equal, nor shall every servant hear My voice in the same way.\n\nFor a prophet hears My voice, while another is moved deep within, while still others may only discern My leading, and this also is according to My will and purpose."},{"align":"center","text":"And that which I do has a perfect work\n\nWithin the hearts of My beloved, coming to\n\nFruition in those who remain in My love..."},{"align":"center","text":"Those meet for The Master’s use..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"in-open-and-in-secret","num":134,"title":"In Open and In Secret","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved, speak not one word concerning those who have hurt you, not one more word against those who have betrayed you. Forgive them, pray for them, and let them go their way. Beloved, love your enemies and pray for those who betray you, and double for those who fight against you, for they have lifted up their heel against Me. Let resentment pass from your heart, and no more let your tongue cause you to stumble on their account. For each is accountable for their own heart and that which flows from it, even to every idle word."},{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, be My examples..."},{"align":"center","text":"Order your speech like David,\n\nAnd conduct yourselves as Daniel..."},{"align":"center","text":"Let your speech express your love for Me\n\nIn every situation, and let your conduct reveal\n\nMy spirit in you, in open and in secret..."},{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, prepare as though I were\n\nComing to take you this very day;\n\nWalk with Me as though we walk\n\nTogether in the Garden already..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"doers-of-the-word","num":135,"title":"Doers of the Word","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"In repentance I am always well pleased..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore let the penitent now turn fully to God,\n\nAnd do works meet for repentance..."},{"align":"center","text":"Let them no more be as the hypocrite,\n\nBut let them walk close behind Me,\n\nAbiding in the shadow of The Almighty..."},{"align":"center","text":"And what more shall I speak than\n\nThat which I have spoken already?..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore believe My words, and also do them..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"a-true-disciple","num":136,"title":"A True Disciple","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The power of My strength shall be\n\nFulfilled in My servant’s weakness,\n\nIn accordance with their love and faithfulness,\n\nAnd by their willingness to lay down their life,\n\nThat they might receive of My life..."},{"align":"center","text":"A man in desperate thirst who refuses every cup\n\nFrom men, yet gladly drinks from Mine..."},{"align":"center","text":"A man whose hunger has brought forth\n\nWithin him a great void, which can not\n\nBe filled by any earthly bread..."},{"align":"center","text":"A man who strives to live by every word\n\nThat proceeds from the mouth of God..."},{"align":"center","text":"A man who carries Me within him, bearing the\n\nScars of My Passion in his heart, always..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"serve-me-as-i-have-loved-you","num":137,"title":"Serve Me As I Have Loved You","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"From this field I have called a select few, to be My examples; not according to their own righteousness, nor by their own strength or intellect, but according to My Word and by My spirit which dwells within them. These have forsaken everything for the sake of their Shepherd. They follow Me wheresoever I go. They listen to My voice and heed the call, and will by no means follow another."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, you also shall strive to be My examples..."},{"align":"center","text":"Beloved ones, serve Me as I have loved you..."},{"align":"center","text":"And remember, whatsoever you do\n\nFor another, you have done it for Me;\n\nAnd whatsoever you do to another,\n\nWhether in goodness or in malice,\n\nYou have done it also to Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-narrow-way","num":138,"title":"The Narrow Way","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"I have indeed bestowed upon this generation a multitude of gifts, a great number of words, words of warning and unsurpassed wisdom, words of exaltation and correction, calling all in the earth to repent.\n\nLo, I have expounded many words of unending love, with great passion, revealing My Mercy which endures forever. Behold, I have proclaimed the way of salvation, time and time again, and He whose name is The Salvation of God! Yes, I have blown the trumpet and called forth My watchmen, I have struck the gates and rattled the doors, I have shaken the foundations of the earth! And still the people hold fast, clutching the pillars and shoring up the doors against Me!"},{"align":"center","text":"Yet from the beginning I established the line,\n\nA narrow way which I had placed in the\n\nMidst of My people, Israel..."},{"align":"center","text":"And in My mercy, I revealed The Way\n\nIn which My people should walk..."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, even now I have placed a\n\nPlumb line in the midst of all people,\n\nSetting all these crooked paths straight..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am The Lord, and I do not change."}]},{"id":"the-perfect-sacrifice","num":139,"title":"The Perfect Sacrifice","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Behold, I had come to you as a man,\n\nClothed in the flesh, humble, My glory set aside;\n\nGod become man, Immanu El..."},{"align":"center","text":"Living as all have lived in the body,\n\nYet not as man lives in the spirit;\n\nFor I am clean, having no sin in My body,\n\nNor in My spirit, having obeyed every\n\nCommand of The Father - blameless..."},{"align":"center","text":"The Lamb of God without spot or blemish,\n\nSent to die for the sins of the world,\n\nBearing the full weight of\n\nTransgression in My own body..."},{"align":"center","text":"The perfect sacrifice, acceptable to God,\n\nWhereby all men are reconciled to The Father,\n\nIf they so choose to receive of The Free Gift\n\nAnd walk in My ways..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"the-victory","num":140,"title":"The Victory","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"All those who repent in My name, with\n\nSincere remorse in their hearts, are saved..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am The One who makes it\n\nPossible for them to do so..."},{"align":"center","text":"And though some have fallen asleep in death,\n\nAnd others are slain, even by their own hand,\n\nI ask you, shall death have the last word?..."},{"align":"center","text":"BY NO MEANS!\n\nFor I shall raise them up at the Last Day!..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I have granted them the victory, even as\n\nI am The Victory, being The Firstfruits from death..."},{"align":"center","text":"Even as those given Me shall likewise be first\n\nWhen the shout is made..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"search-not-in-the-world","num":141,"title":"Search Not in the World","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"My grace descends upon all who repent in sincerity and in truth, and My spirit dwells within those who keep The Commandments and testify to My glory. Therefore, receive of Me; then will that which you seek become clear. For your heart’s true desire can not be found in the world... _Seek God!_"},{"align":"center","text":"Again I say to you, search not in the world,\n\nFor there you will not find Me;\n\nNor seek Me in the churches of men,\n\nFor there you will not find Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I tell you the truth,\n\nThe Kingdom of God is within you..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"ingress","num":142,"title":"Ingress","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved ones, give your attention to those things I have set before you, obey all My commands, and consider that which I require of you... _Trust in Me._\n\nRun not ahead, nor lag behind, but grow wise in My ways. Keep your eyes fixed upon Me, and be keenly aware of My goings out and comings in... _Follow Me._"},{"align":"center","text":"Yet remember this..."},{"align":"center","text":"The state of your heart\n\nDictates how much you receive,\n\nAnd your obedience decides the ingress..."},{"align":"center","text":"Your willingness sets the pace, and the strength\n\nOf your grip will keep you from falling..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-commandments","num":143,"title":"The Commandments","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"In My love, I laid for you an everlasting\n\nFoundation upon which you were to stand..."},{"align":"center","text":"And in My mercy I constructed high walls,\n\nMade with the finest stone, to protect you,\n\nEven from yourselves..."},{"align":"center","text":"Engraven stones,\n\nTouched by the finger of God..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"my-spirit-dwells-in-my-own","num":144,"title":"My Spirit Dwells in My Own","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved ones, I tell you the truth, the people of this world do not know Me. Therefore I have come close, to unstop the ears of all who long to hear My voice and obey it; I have drawn near, to open the eyes of all who desire to look upon My face and partake of My glory; and behold, I have poured out My spirit to restore the hearts of the penitent, to breathe new life into all those who embrace My words and seek to remain in My love."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am come, and have come already;\n\nAnd behold, I shall also return\n\nAnd reveal My glory..."},{"align":"center","text":"I have not departed from My people,\n\nFor My spirit dwells in My own..."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet all must be broken..."},{"align":"center","text":"Some broken before the time,\n\nAnd many more after..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"restored","num":145,"title":"Restored","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Once you were lost, yet now you are found..."},{"align":"center","text":"Once you were naked, yet now you are clothed\n\nIn fine linens of white, your filthy rags cast off forever..."},{"align":"center","text":"Once you were hungry and very thirsty, starving\n\nIn a world of empty promises, lies and vain deceits,\n\nYet now you are nourished with The Word of Truth..."},{"align":"center","text":"Once you were sick, mortally ill,\n\nYet now you are healed in Me, now you are\n\nRestored because of Me - My body, My bride..."},{"align":"center","text":"My precious flower, My pleasant plant, of which\n\nI shall pluck from the earth at the time appointed,\n\nReplanted in the Garden at dawn on the new day..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore come forth, all My people,\n\nAnd flourish in the light of The Lord,\n\nAnd bear much fruit in The Beloved!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"a-spear-and-a-sword","num":146,"title":"A Spear and a Sword","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"My every Letter is a spear with which I\n\nShall pierce the heart of this people..."},{"align":"center","text":"Every Volume a sword by which I\n\nShall divide them asunder..."},{"align":"center","text":"A rod and a staff for those who believe..."},{"align":"center","text":"I AM THE LORD."}]},{"id":"contentions","num":147,"title":"Contentions","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Answer not the obstinate, nor strive\n\nWith those who reject My words..."},{"align":"center","text":"Give no occasion to the adversary,\n\nNor give the mocker a voice;\n\nGive the scoffer no consideration at all;\n\nLet them eat silence..."},{"align":"center","text":"Rather pray for your adversaries..."},{"align":"center","text":"For they do not fight against you,\n\nThey contend with Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"labor-of-love","num":148,"title":"Labor of Love","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved ones, treat those of My body as you wish to be treated. Consider not what tomorrow may bring, nor dwell on that which has passed; embrace them as they are in this moment. For the one who stands in front of you is the person they are today. For who they were yesterday has passed away, and the person they will become tomorrow is not yet revealed. For you know not what tomorrow will bring, nor do you truly know that which has passed. You know neither the heart nor the mind, nor are you able to search the thoughts or look upon the innermost intentions.\n\nTherefore, treat all My beloved as you would treat Me. Embrace your brothers and sisters in Messiah as you would embrace Me, walking with Me as I am and not as you would have Me be. For it is written: _According to the judgment with which you judge shall you be judged, and with the measure you use shall it be measured back to you._"},{"align":"center","text":"Yet the servant who walks with Me\n\nMoment by moment, treating their\n\nBrother or sister as they wish to be treated,\n\nShall walk free, unhindered..."},{"align":"center","text":"Their every reasonable service\n\nBecoming a labor of love..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"do-not-judge","num":149,"title":"Do Not Judge","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"It is written: _Do not speak evil of one another. For whoever speaks evil of a brother, or judges a brother, speaks evil of The Law and judges The Law. But if you judge The Law, you are not a doer of what The Law says, but a judge. {{ref:James 4:11}}_"},{"align":"center","text":"In the same way, one who speaks evil\n\nOf My messenger and judges My prophet\n\nSpeaks evil of Me and judges the Word..."},{"align":"center","text":"And one who judges the Word will\n\nBy no means obey it, but have set\n\nThemselves up as an authority, a judge,\n\nHeld captive by their own evil thoughts."},{"align":"justify","text":"Again, one who refuses My messenger can by no means receive My message, and one who judges him has blinded themselves to the Truth. For there is none righteous, no, not one. Yet The One who sent the message is true. Thus the one who delivers My Word must also be its recipient, or how shall I send him? And all those who judge can do nothing and shall receive nothing; even that which they have shall be taken away, says The Lord."}]},{"id":"spiritual-warriors","num":150,"title":"Spiritual Warriors","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"What is man? He is but flesh, his power of no use at all. And in his pride he seeks glory for himself, a false valor. And so he continually turns to his own devices, deceiving himself, thinking he stands though he has fallen.\n\nFoolhardy, he rushes into battle where he suffers injury after injury, ignoring his wounds, wounds which remain unhealed, infecting the whole of the body. Yet he continues on in his arrogance, his pride driving him forward, unable to see that he is cast down, saying within himself, “Look at my accomplishments, look upon all I have done!” And all the while satan laughs, saying, _“Behold my acolytes; see how these men of battle have become like me.”_"},{"align":"center","text":"Sons and daughters of men, you are no warriors..."},{"align":"center","text":"You are casualties, spoils of a war\n\nWhich was won from the foundation\n\nOf the world, of which I was also slain..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I alone bear the scars of battle..."},{"align":"center","text":"Lo, I bear them in My hands and My feet,\n\nUpon My back and in My side, wounds which I\n\nReceived in the house of My friends..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"an-ensign-to-all-nations","num":151,"title":"An Ensign to All Nations","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Let the Trumpet be blown loudly!\n\nLet the call to repentance go out\n\nAnd the announcement be made!..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I have lifted up an ensign to all nations,\n\nI have set up a standard for this sleeping generation..."},{"align":"center","text":"A bright and shining lamppost for My people..."},{"align":"center","text":"A light, the glory of which shall not be diminished,\n\nBut shall only increase by measure..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"pure-works","num":152,"title":"Pure Works","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved ones, worship Me as I am and not as you would have Me be! Obey MY voice! Depart from every form of evil and tear down every whitewashed wall of abomination!\n\nAgain, I say, be separate and come out from among them, and repent! Return to Me, in spirit and in truth, and in the day I stretch out My hand against the inhabitants of the earth, you shall surely be gone from this place.\n\nMy beloved servants, share your gifts: Lift up the poor and help the needy, give drink to the thirsty and feed the hungry, share My love and wash each other’s feet. Yet no longer be a friend of this world, and no more walk in the ways of the churches of men, for they have not known Me."},{"align":"center","text":"Be set apart! Rejoice and give thanks!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Honor The Messiah in spirit and in truth,\n\nAnd walk closely in His example;\n\nTestify of Him, from His birth to His passion;\n\nGlorify His name in all the earth!..."},{"align":"center","text":"For HE is the true gift..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"escape","num":153,"title":"Escape","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Embrace My words, obey that which I have\n\nSpoken to this generation, and you shall surely\n\nEscape all these things which I am about to do."},{"align":"center","text":"For as it was in the days of Lot, when I brought\n\nHim out of the city, so likewise shall I deliver\n\nMy people in the Day of Wrath."},{"align":"center","text":"For those in whom The Messiah\n\nDwells must be taken out of the way;\n\nThen shall I judge the earth and strike the nations."},{"align":"center","text":"For I do not change..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-wrath-of-god","num":154,"title":"The Wrath of God","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Beloved ones, come to Me, and I shall give you rest;\n\nBe drawn to Me, that I may lift you up."},{"align":"center","text":"For I tell you the truth, My wrath is coming;\n\nBehold, My anger is aroused, My fierce\n\nJealousy burns like a raging fire\n\nAnd is about to come to the full."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet do not waver, but understand."},{"align":"center","text":"For My wrath is required, and the foundation\n\nOf My anger rests solidly upon My jealousy,\n\nBy which My unending sorrow is also revealed."},{"align":"center","text":"For My wrath is born of sorrow,\n\nAnd My anger bursts forth as a husband\n\nJealous over his bride, My fury as a father\n\nProtecting his children, as one mighty\n\nIn battle breaking through the lines..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"a-dry-tree","num":155,"title":"A Dry Tree","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"What is a dry tree to he who holds the axe?"},{"align":"center","text":"Yet when the winds pass through and catch\n\nThe man sleeping, is he not easily\n\nCrushed by the weight of the tree?"},{"align":"center","text":"Indeed, what is this forest full of tall trees\n\nBefore Me, standing so tall with roots deeply\n\nEmbedded in the world, blocking always the warmth\n\nOf the sun at eventide, casting long shadows\n\nUnder which the wicked flock?"},{"align":"center","text":"Are they not soon left cold, standing in darkness?"},{"align":"center","text":"Are they not as those who seek shelter under a tree\n\nWhen the rains descend and the thunder crashes,\n\nWho meet a quick end when lightning strikes?..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-plight-of-the-ungodly","num":156,"title":"The Plight of the Ungodly","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The words of scoffers come forth\n\nFrom a hard and troubled heart,\n\nFrom a place void of understanding."},{"align":"center","text":"Their words are like chaff, their every lofty\n\nAssertion dust, carried away by the wind."},{"align":"center","text":"As a ship tossed about by rough seas,\n\nSo is the plight of the ungodly;\n\nIn a dark sea of confusion, they attempt\n\nTo sail against every wind of doctrine\n\nWhich opposes them."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet all their toil is in vain..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am The Only Truth!\nI am God alone!"}]},{"id":"indomitable","num":157,"title":"Indomitable","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Behold, all I have spoken\n\nIs established and shall be;\n\nMy Word yields to no man."},{"align":"center","text":"For My words are poured out like rain,\n\nAnd My voice shakes the house like thunder,\n\nMy every word a hailstone released from\n\nThe treasury of hail, which I have\n\nReserved for the Time of Trouble."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, My wrath is a consuming fire,\n\nA mighty earthquake, encompassing\n\nThe breadth of the whole earth!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-weeping-willow","num":158,"title":"The Weeping Willow","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"What is the high branch of the palm tree\n\nTo that of the weeping willow?\n\nFor they know not each other’s place."},{"align":"center","text":"Each bears seed after its own kind,\n\nYet the ground beneath remains unyielding.\n\nAnd without the rain, the leaf fades\n\nAnd the seed flees back into the dust\n\nOf the ground, unable to rise again."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore are they cut down as the cedars;\n\nThey are broken and they are toppled when\n\nCalamity comes to claim them, washed away."},{"align":"center","text":"And who will mourn their passing or\n\nSearch out their seed, that they might\n\nBe revived in another place?..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"cast-down","num":159,"title":"Cast Down","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Is My Word in need of confirmation by those who say they know Me, yet do not really know Me? Is the Word of My mouth subject to men, whose understanding remains altogether lacking, whose knowledge is corrupt and whose power is of no use at all?\n\nShall My words be made subject to the approval of any self- appointed apostle, prophet or teacher? Shall flesh usurp the things of God? Can mortal man ascend above the throne of The Eternal? Shall the created rule over The Creator, or the corrupt sit as judge over The Holy? Shall any attempt to occupy My throne and not be cast down?!"},{"align":"center","text":"Thus the highly esteemed shall be abandoned,\n\nAnd the self-appointed severely abased..."},{"align":"center","text":"Left to walk through the valley in the\n\nGreat and Terrible Day of The Lord,\n\nUntil death comes to claim them..."},{"align":"center","text":"Declares The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-doctrines-of-men","num":160,"title":"The Doctrines of Men","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The doctrines of men are a\n\nLoathsome spot on every garment\n\nWorn in the name of truth!..."},{"align":"center","text":"A detestable wrinkle within\n\nThe tapestry of My glory!..."},{"align":"center","text":"A horrible interwoven thread by\n\nWhich those who call of themselves\n\nChristian pollute My name and mar\n\nMy image before the people..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"my-hand-is-removed","num":161,"title":"My Hand Is Removed","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The penitent wait and\n\nBow down in thanksgiving."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet the arrogant and false righteous\n\nStand up proudly, declaring their\n\nDeliverance, a deliverance which has\n\nAlready passed and shall not come."},{"align":"center","text":"For My hand is removed\n\nAnd My spirit taken."},{"align":"center","text":"For only those in whom I see of Myself\n\nShall escape, and only those caught\n\nIn My embrace shall fly away..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"i-am-god-of-the-living","num":162,"title":"I Am God of the Living","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"There is a people who sleep and a flesh which has no life in it, there are many who have been lost to the depths, a great multitude who have returned to the dust of the earth and can not be found. Yet The Lord God knows their names and their dwelling places; not one has passed from My sight, not one has been given up to the void."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, the day and hour is close at hand,\n\nYea it is very near, when the dead in Messiah\n\nShall arise and the sleepers shall awake,\n\nWhen the rotting corpses are revived\n\nAnd the dust gathers together once again..."},{"align":"center","text":"From one end of the earth to the other,\n\nEven from the deepest depths, shall My people\n\nRise up and give Me glory!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore let the children of Israel prepare,\n\nLet everyone joined to Messiah step forward\n\nAnd claim their inheritance..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I have but to call out your name!....\n\n\n\nFor I am God of the living,\n\nThe One alone worthy of all praise..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Holy One of Israel."}]},{"id":"the-indignation-of-the-lord","num":163,"title":"The Indignation of The Lord","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"My anger is kindled and\n\nBurns in the heat of My wrath;\n\nMy indignation has come to the full\n\nAnd must be poured out!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Like a dark storm building upon\n\nThe horizon brings foreboding,\n\nAs a great torrent inundates a city and\n\nRunning waters quickly overtake a town..."},{"align":"center","text":"Like fierce waves beat back the shore\n\nOr a raging sea capsizes a ship,\n\nAs the power of the great whirlwind\n\nCauses widespread devastation..."},{"align":"center","text":"So shall the indignation of The Lord be!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"a-broadsword","num":164,"title":"A Broadsword","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The name of The Lord of Hosts is a broadsword,\n\nAnd My every word a freshly sharpened blade!\n\nFor in My name is great power, and at the sound\n\nOf My name all darkness flees away!"},{"align":"center","text":"For as a razor removes the stubble,\n\nAnd fervent heat burns away the dross,\n\nSo shall My name purge the waste places\n\nAnd cleanse the polluted cities..."},{"align":"center","text":"Until all these squawking birds are brought\n\nDown into silence and every tall tower\n\nIs toppled and left in ruins!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Until Babel is utterly destroyed and every\n\nLast vestige of man’s invention is wiped\n\nFrom the face of the earth!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord God."}]},{"id":"signs","num":165,"title":"Signs","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Many great signs have been given\n\nTo this generation, yet all have went\n\nGreatly ignored by the multitude;\n\nYet those who are Mine have clearly seen."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet understand this,\n\nThese signs are but the first of many,\n\nAnd shall continue, increasing by measure\n\nUntil the time be fulfilled..."},{"align":"center","text":"Then shall The Son of Man appear,\n\nClothed in the brightness of His glory,\n\nA brilliance which has no equal;\n\nEven the blind shall see!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"in-my-footsteps","num":166,"title":"In My Footsteps","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved, I delight in that which one gives to another in My name, and by the works of their own hands and feet in all righteousness. This is the tithe in which I delight most.\n\nTherefore if one comes to you, saying, _“Give me a cup of water,”_ give them a drink in My name. And if another comes, saying, _“I need a shirt, for I am naked and cold,”_ give them your shirt and your coat also. And if this same one asks, _“Will you walk with me this far?”_ Go with them double."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, tithe not only\n\nOf your money and material possessions,\n\nBut also of your strength and your time,\n\nAs one willing to give up their life for My sake."},{"align":"center","text":"For this is to truly know Me,\n\nThis is to walk in Me, in My very footsteps,\n\nAnd to love your neighbor as yourself..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"the-way-of-the-upright","num":167,"title":"The Way of the Upright","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Those who have received eyes to see,\n\nSee the way ahead clearly and\n\nWithout obstruction, and follow it."},{"align":"center","text":"And those who have received ears to hear,\n\nHear the Truth and obey it..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"a-welcomed-rain","num":168,"title":"A Welcomed Rain","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved, I have poured out My spirit on all flesh, even as I was poured out for you from the beginning. Yet no one comes to drink, not one is willing to receive of Me as I truly am. Therefore I shall indeed remove My hand, and My spirit shall return to Me. Behold, from every individual who refuses to give heed to My voice and embrace My correction has it departed already.\n\nYet let all those who remain in My love understand and have peace. For though My spirit departs from the multitudes and the ensuing darkness be thick, though wickedness overflows and every man of pride who being wise in his own eyes is left confounded, I shall not make a total end."},{"align":"center","text":"For My hand shall remain with the faithful,\n\nAnd My strength shall be revealed in My anointed."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, My spirit shall well up within\n\nThe hearts of the penitent and come upon\n\nMy chosen as a welcomed rain, and they shall\n\nBe greatly increased, shining ever brighter,\n\nEven amidst thick clouds and darkness..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"prepare-the-way-of-the-lord","num":169,"title":"Prepare the Way of The Lord","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Prepare in the desert the way of The Lord!\n\nMake a straight path in these\n\nDry and parched lands,\n\nFor The Holy One of Israel!"},{"align":"center","text":"Let every valley be exalted,\n\nAnd every mountain and hill brought low!\n\nLet the crooked places be made straight,\n\nAnd the rough places smooth!"},{"align":"center","text":"For The Glory of The Lord shall be\n\nRevealed from Heaven, and all\n\nPeople shall behold it together!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Declares The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-joy-of-the-lord","num":170,"title":"The Joy of The Lord","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Beloved, come and be filled with the joy of The Lord, which never fades, nor does it slumber, nor will it ever pass away; a flood of joy flowing into the innermost parts of your being, cascading through your spirit, reaching deep into that hidden place known only to The Lord; a place crafted by My own fingertips, delicately fashioned so those of the flesh may know Me, unlocked and opened by the trusting in and the knowledge of The Greatest of All Loves..."},{"align":"justify","text":"A love which surpasses time and space, life and death, a place of perfect peace, yea inside pure and undefiled love; love of such a kind, cleansing every part seen and unseen, known and unknown; the love of such power and majesty, even that which has been corrupted is restored in the image of God... From grace to Grace, from light to The Light..."},{"align":"justify","text":"My glory shown in you and through you, bright and shining, a flame brought forth from My own glory, shared with My beloved forever; a flame which can never be put out, nor can it flicker, nor shall it be covered over again! For where I am there is no darkness at all! Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"a-trumpet-and-alarm","num":171,"title":"A Trumpet and Alarm","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Let all who behold My words look upon\n\nThem as an ensign, as a waving banner brought\n\nForth and set up for this wayward generation,\n\nEven as a trumpet and alarm blowing\n\nContinually upon the wall..."},{"align":"center","text":"Let its sound rush through the streets of the cities!\n\nLet its noise be carried into the wilderness,\n\nEven to the outermost isles!"},{"align":"center","text":"And let all those who have ears to hear listen,\n\nAnd be silent before their God, and pray."},{"align":"center","text":"Indeed, let all in the earth partake of My Word\n\nAnd be brought into deep and profound silence,\n\nAnd consider..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-stone","num":172,"title":"The Stone","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I shall increase the sound of\n\nMy voice seven times, even as Jericho,\n\nUntil all things break and all are broken..."},{"align":"center","text":"Many broken unto death, ground to dust\n\nBeneath The Stone which shall be placed in Zion,\n\nFor The Stone shall become a great mountain\n\nFilling the whole earth..."},{"align":"center","text":"While still others, My hidden treasure,\n\nMy battered and bruised sheep,\n\nThe wild of My flock, are broken and\n\nCome to rest solidly atop this same Stone,\n\nThe Rock of My Enduring Promise..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-lord-your-righteousness","num":173,"title":"The Lord Your Righteousness","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"The Lord your God has a Holy One. He is The Head of the body, The True Sanctuary, The Only Life Without End! Behold, He is a strong tower, a fortified city in the day of battle, an all-encompassing fire, The Mighty and Strong One whose rod is made of iron, The Law-Giver... The Source of Life by which all things consist, your Carpenter and Redeemer, The Salvation of God!\n\nTherefore wait upon The Lord with meekness and fear, with unwavering trust; wait for Him! For He is The Fountain of Living Waters for all who thirst, a fruitful vine for the hungry, a wealth of riches for all those who come to Me empty."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, beloved, give Him glory!\n\nLift up your voices with everlasting praise!\n\nBring thanksgiving to the altar,\n\nAnd offer up your hearts before Him!"},{"align":"center","text":"Shout His name to the heavens,\n\nFor He is The Lord your Righteousness!..."},{"align":"center","text":"YAHUSHUA HAMASHIACH!..."},{"align":"center","text":"IMMANU EL!"}]},{"id":"the-voice-of-the-lord","num":174,"title":"The Voice of The Lord","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"And what of My voice, you ask? Its sound? Its tone? Its passion?\n\nThis is what I say to you: Listen, and you shall also know..."},{"align":"center","text":"How does water taste to the man\n\nLost in the desert, dying of thirst?"},{"align":"center","text":"How does food taste to the starving?"},{"align":"center","text":"How does love feel to the desolate?"},{"align":"center","text":"How does the warmth of a fire feel\n\nTo those coming in from the cold?"},{"align":"center","text":"How does the caress of your\n\nBeloved feel after many days apart?"},{"align":"center","text":"How does a father look upon his newborn child?"},{"align":"center","text":"How can one describe the sound\n\nOf love which surpasses knowledge,\n\nThe sound of what My love is?"},{"align":"center","text":"Can you hold the infinite in your hand?!"},{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, this is what My voice\n\nSounds like to those who love Me:"},{"align":"center","text":"A still small voice."},{"align":"center","text":"And to the rest:\n\nThe sound of rushing waters,\n\nLightnings and thunderings of fury and fiery anger,\n\nWith deep and infinite sorrow, bitter anguish!"},{"align":"center","text":"Love."},{"align":"center","text":"The Voice of Truth."}]},{"id":"the-volumes","num":175,"title":"The Volumes","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"My Word in The Volumes of Truth is the rod by which the translations of men are to be tested, a light which shines upon the doctrines of men to expose them, revealing them to be blasphemies and heresies before God, all of which shall burn up in the Day, when the fire comes to test the quality of each man’s work."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, if one professing faith be wise,\n\nHe shall humble himself before Me,\n\nCalling upon the name of The Holy One\n\nFor knowledge, in where all understanding\n\nFlows to the truly contrite and penitent,\n\nFlowing in pure testimony, free from corruption."},{"align":"center","text":"And by this only shall one be wise in the reading,\n\nComparing that which was given with that\n\nWhich is put forth once again, discerning\n\nThe Source and The Author to be the same..."},{"align":"center","text":"One Word, One Book,\n\nOne on-going Testament to My glory;\n\nBy no means shall it be divided into three!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-tabernacle-of-my-mercy","num":176,"title":"The Tabernacle of My Mercy","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Behold, I shall come in an instant!\n\nIn a moment, I shall reach down and take My spoil!"},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, let the remnant of Israel be found\n\nWaiting with eager hands, and let those grafted\n\nInto My olive tree bear summer fruit!"},{"align":"center","text":"Let the sprigs sprout quickly,\n\nAnd let not the seedlings be withered;\n\nLet not the noonday sun wilt or scorch\n\nAny of My pleasant plants."},{"align":"center","text":"Be moved from your places,\n\nOh My people, and be hidden!\n\nBe exalted, oh My beautiful ones,\n\nAnd find sanctuary in the tabernacle of My mercy!"},{"align":"center","text":"Be sheltered from all this burning heat,\n\nUntil the indignation passes by\n\nAnd The Majesty comes! {{ref:Isaiah 26:20-21}}..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-only-judge","num":177,"title":"The Only Judge","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Nothing coming from the mouth of those who scoff and shoot out the lip against The Lord’s anointed, whether they be a friend or an enemy, a spouse or a relative, a neighbor or a stranger, a scholar or a teacher, a pastor or a self-appointed prophet or preacher, shall be accounted as true. Neither shall any weight be given to their arguments; it is wind. For I alone sit as judge, says The Lord."}]},{"id":"brought-low","num":178,"title":"Brought Low","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"As the scythe cuts through the stalk,\n\nAs the sweeping blow fells many plants at once,\n\nSo shall the sharpness of realization cut to the heart\n\nOf this people, and in that same moment the\n\nLoftiness of many shall be brought down..."},{"align":"center","text":"Declares The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-author-and-the-finisher","num":179,"title":"The Author and The Finisher","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"If you embrace the Scriptures of Truth,\n\nYet reject My Word in these Volumes,\n\nYou deny the Word of The Lord."},{"align":"center","text":"And if you embrace My Letters,\n\nYet reject the Bible,\n\nYou deny the Word of The Lord."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am The Author and Finisher thereof..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"solace","num":180,"title":"Solace","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I shall not make a total end..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I shall clothe all who come to Me\n\nIn sincere repentance with fine robes."},{"align":"center","text":"I shall feed the poor in spirit,\n\nWipe the tears of the remorseful,\n\nAnd uphold the broken."},{"align":"center","text":"I shall shelter the penitent and give grace\n\nTo the humble, and the pure in heart\n\nShall behold My face."},{"align":"center","text":"Indeed, all who wash My feet\n\nWith their tears shall be comforted\n\nFor one week in the house of The Lord..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Holy One of Israel."}]},{"id":"the-almighty","num":181,"title":"The Almighty","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"I AM THE LORD..."},{"align":"center","text":"He who sets up kingdoms and brings them to ruin!\n\nHe who set the foundations of the earth\n\nAnd covered them with beauty!\n\nHe who also set the stars in their places\n\nAnd caused the galaxies to take their form!\n\nHe to whom all creation bows down!..."},{"align":"center","text":"He whose power is limitless and by whose wisdom\n\nAll things were brought forth,\n\nWhose authority is absolute,\n\nThe God who reigns in Israel!..."},{"align":"center","text":"He who was and is and is to come,\n\nThe Almighty!"}]},{"id":"refinement","num":182,"title":"Refinement","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"The lake of My burning heart is a consuming fire,\n\nAnd in the heat of My jealousy I shall purify\n\nMy people seven times, until only that\n\nWhich bears My likeness remains..."},{"align":"center","text":"The refined lifted up, the wicked consumed,\n\nDestruction of every kind of evil!..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am The Lord who was and is,\n\nEven from the beginning,\n\nAnd to the end and forever after I remain..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-planting-of-the-lord","num":183,"title":"The Planting of The Lord","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Pretense is not at all becoming of a servant\n\nOf The Lord; neither is the world a garment\n\nWhich My elect shall wear."},{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, strip yourselves naked;\n\nCast off these filthy robes!\n\nWash yourselves, make yourselves clean!\n\nTurn away from this world, and come to Me!"},{"align":"center","text":"Lay yourselves upon the altar and\n\nBecome a living sacrifice to The Lord,\n\nThe planting of The Lord, My pleasant plants\n\nSet in the midst of My vineyard,\n\nMy beautiful ones grafted in..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"a-unique-and-lovely-song","num":184,"title":"A Unique and Lovely Song","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Here is wisdom: The prayers of My children are indeed precious in My sight, a unique and lovely song entering My ears. For every song sung in My name, whether in open or in secret, in sorrow or in joy, is received up to Heaven as a memorial before The Holy One of Israel, even as incense before the altar. For that which has come up before Me is a blessing, which is then received back again, a wonderful recompense for fervent prayer on another’s behalf."},{"align":"center","text":"Thus that prayed due to a troubled heart\n\nComes back again, to heal not the heart\n\nOf the one on whose behalf the prayer was offered,\n\nBut to mend that which is torn in the\n\nHeart of the one who offered it..."},{"align":"center","text":"Whether it be from anger to forgiveness,\n\nOr from anguish to peace,\n\nOr from tears of sadness to tears\n\nOf hope and joyful expectation..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"a-prophet","num":185,"title":"A Prophet","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"What is a prophet?..."},{"align":"center","text":"Is he not a man, My servant,\n\nWhom I have chosen and called?\n\nAnd when does My servant become a prophet?\n\nAnd what is the length of time he remains as such?"},{"align":"center","text":"Lo, he is only a prophet in that self-same moment\n\nIn which I speak to him and cause him to hear,\n\nProphesying only as long as I cause him\n\nTo speak or to write My words."},{"align":"center","text":"For there is no prophecy apart from My will,\n\nAnd without My voice there can be no prophesying;\n\nAnd without My spirit, no man may hear,\n\nNor shall he behold a vision,\n\nNor is he able to understand."},{"align":"center","text":"Apart from The Holy One,\n\nThere is no knowledge..."},{"align":"center","text":"I AM THE LORD."}]},{"id":"no-equal","num":186,"title":"No Equal","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"I am The Lord, He who stretched out the heavens and hung the earth upon nothing. I am He who created all these worlds, He who causes all things to be. I am He who formed man from the dust of the earth and gave him breath, and he became a living soul. Behold, I spoke all life into existence, yes, I am He who called all things into existence, saying, _“Arise and declare My glory!”_ For all creation obeys the sound of My voice."},{"align":"center","text":"Yea, the whole universe declares My glory!\n\nFor I am He who commanded the stars to shine\n\nTheir light and the galaxies to take their form."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, My voice reaches across the universe,\n\nAnd reverence is spread out before Me;\n\nFor I command the hills to bow down and the\n\nMountains to be brought low, and it is so;\n\nYea, the whole earth trembles when I pass by!"},{"align":"center","text":"For I am great in power and My glory has no equal!"},{"align":"center","text":"Thus the fear of The Lord goes before Me,\n\nAnd obedience follows after Me..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"maranatha","num":187,"title":"Maranatha","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Fear God and put all your trust in The Holy One. For the power of The Father is displayed through The Son, for He is the express image of The Holy, The Salvation of God... _He whose hand reaches far and wide, whose strength is almighty, whose wisdom holds all creation in His understanding, whose love endures forever! He whose righteousness comes, and had been stretched out before us, for every eye to see! The end of which shall be as a flood cleansing the sanctuary of His mercy, restoring all things, even to a new heavens and a new earth._"},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, it is time for the power\n\nOf God to be made known, for the name\n\nOf The Holy One of Israel to be glorified\n\nAbove the heights of the mountains,\n\nTo overshadow every hill!..."},{"align":"center","text":"It is time for The King to return and gather,\n\nTo reveal the glory of His might!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Immanu El!"}]},{"id":"trust-in-god-alone","num":188,"title":"Trust In God Alone","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"What is earthly, let it stay earthly;\n\nAnd what is spiritual, let it stay spiritual."},{"align":"center","text":"Hold not to the earthly nor to the\n\nUnderstanding of men, nor grab hold\n\nOf any private interpretation of Scripture;\n\nTrust not in the doctrines of men."},{"align":"center","text":"Hold fast to God,\n\nAnd place all your trust in The Messiah."}]},{"id":"open-your-eyes-to-the-truth","num":189,"title":"Open Your Eyes to The Truth","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Search, and you shall discover the truth, which is God. Dissect life’s structures; there He is, its writer and fashioner. Look deeper and farther than ever before, and there you will find Him. Calculate and count all things which are before your eyes, yes, search the cosmos, study it, and you will begin to know Him. No matter where you point your lenses, there He is, within the scope of your understanding."},{"align":"center","text":"Behold, all discoveries lead to God!\n\nThough you need not seek, nor discover,\n\nFor the knowledge of God is within you."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet only the shedding of the skin\n\nOf this world and the death of your pride\n\nShall open your eyes to The Truth -\n\nWhich is absolute, forever standing\n\nOn a hill, bright and shining,\n\nImmovable, unbreakable!..."},{"align":"center","text":"The Everlasting Stone which has\n\nBecome The Head of the Corner,\n\nThe Great Mountain which\n\nFills the whole earth!"}]},{"id":"seek-the-light","num":190,"title":"Seek The Light","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Those who seek to understand the dark\n\nWill soon find themselves trapped\n\nIn the midst of it, unable to break free."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet those who seek The Light will find it,\n\nAnd I will show them The Way;\n\nIn these darkness has no foothold..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-redeemed","num":191,"title":"The Redeemed","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Beloved, cast off your sins,\n\nDepart quickly from temptation,\n\nAnd to the accuser turn a deaf ear."},{"align":"center","text":"For I tell you the truth, evil has lost\n\nIts grip on the redeemed..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord YahuShua."}]},{"id":"the-riches-of-eden","num":192,"title":"The Riches of Eden","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Only those in union with The Messiah\n\nShall inherit the riches of Eden,\n\nAnd only those who fully accept\n\nHis sacrifice shall be restored."},{"align":"center","text":"For from the garden did you come forth,\n\nAnd to the garden shall you return;\n\nYet not in the former manner, but in glory..."},{"align":"center","text":"Created anew..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"a-right-heart","num":193,"title":"A Right Heart","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"A right heart bridles the tongue;\n\nAnd a forgiving heart absolves every hurt,\n\nBringing peace to the mind..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"the-restoration","num":194,"title":"The Restoration","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Behold, The Restoration is coming, coming quickly!..."},{"align":"center","text":"All things restored as in the beginning;\n\nA garden where nothing is destroyed,\n\nAnd none are given to destruction;\n\nNo more pain or tears, no more sickness or death..."},{"align":"center","text":"Only life is, and shall be, forever!..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"unchanging","num":195,"title":"Unchanging","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"As I have spoken, so I speak;\n\nAs I am, so shall I be and have always been..."},{"align":"center","text":"For I am The Lord,\n\nAnd I DO NOT CHANGE."}]},{"id":"the-time-of-testing","num":196,"title":"The Time of Testing","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"My spirit has spoken throughout\n\nThe generations, in its steadfastness and quiet;\n\nYet few have ears to hear, few are willing\n\nTo open their hearts and receive My correction."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet now the time has come for those\n\nWho say they are My people to be tried,\n\nIt is time for their works to be tested."},{"align":"center","text":"For the Word of My mouth shall declare it,\n\nAnd in the Day of The Lord\n\nIt shall surely be made plain..."},{"align":"center","text":"Every false way exposed,\n\nEvery perverse tradition torn in pieces,\n\nEvery detestable doctrine crushed\n\nBeneath the weight of the Truth..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"all-tears-wiped-away","num":197,"title":"All Tears Wiped Away","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Those who grab hold of their First Love\n\nWith all their heart, with all their mind,\n\nWith all their strength and with all their soul,\n\nShall never go hungry, nor shall they thirst anymore;\n\nNor shall the heat of the noonday\n\nSun do them any harm..."},{"align":"center","text":"Yea, even all their tears shall be wiped away\n\nIn the house of The Lord..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"tipping-point","num":198,"title":"Tipping Point","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"I tell you the truth, that which is tipped can not be set upright again, and that which has been set in motion can not be stopped. Lo, even that which was held captive in the depths of silence has been released. Behold, it comes forth, increasing by order of magnitude, and can in no wise be put back again... Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"one-salvation","num":199,"title":"One Salvation","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"I have put forth a great multitude of words to bless you, a great number of loving and stern speeches. I have called this generation to repent, and have given ample warning. And those who cupped their ears heard My voice, and those who received of Me wrote My words in their heart, sincerely seeking to do them, that they might honor Me and bring glory to My name."},{"align":"center","text":"For I AM THE LORD,\n\nAnd there is but One Escape..."},{"align":"center","text":"Whether one lives or dies,\n\nThere is but One Salvation..."},{"align":"center","text":"No matter the time or the season,\n\nThere is but One..."},{"align":"center","text":"Declares The Almighty."}]},{"id":"trust","num":200,"title":"Trust","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Behold, the signs of My coming\n\nAre made plain and are revealed in the\n\nWorld everyday, even in every corner."},{"align":"center","text":"Yet that which I am doing is not\n\nEasily discerned by men;\n\nFor their hearts are hard, and they\n\nRemain slow of understanding."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore great trust is required,\n\nAnd must be born of real belief,\n\nKnowing I AM WHO I AM..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord."}]},{"id":"acquiesce","num":201,"title":"Acquiesce","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"Listen to the sound of My voice,\n\nFall in love with Me as at the first,\n\nCome to Me anew as in the beginning;\n\nBeloved, it is time to acquiesce,\n\nTo fully surrender to the truth of who I am!..."},{"align":"center","text":"To be submersed in My spirit,\n\nTo be baptized in My love,\n\nTo seek first The Kingdom of God\n\nAnd His Righteousness, which I am..."},{"align":"center","text":"Then shall that which is needful be added to you..."},{"align":"center","text":"I AM THE LORD."}]},{"id":"the-lord-s-day","num":202,"title":"The Lord’s Day","paragraphs":[{"align":"justify","text":"Behold, The Son of Righteousness shall rise up with healing in His wings, and you, My precious beloved, shall go out leaping like calves released from the stall! The King, Himself, shall cultivate the ground in that day, with streams of living waters breaking out behind Him! Behold, new life shall fill every corner, and the desolate places shall be restored! Whole forests shall burst forth from the ground, with every kind of tree and flowering plant, every kind of grass and fern reappearing, and every living creature leaping up from the dust of the earth, once again!\n\nBehold, The Lord’s peace shall be there! And nothing under the sun shall destroy, nor shall anything be given to destruction, in all My holy mountain! For there shall be no predator, nor shall any prey be found, neither shall the strong slay the weak. For as it is written: _The wolf and the lamb shall feed together, the lion shall eat straw like the ox, and dust shall be the serpent’s food. {{ref:Isaiah 65:25}}_ All shall dwell in safety, with every living creature dwelling at peace with its neighbor.\n\nBehold, in that day everlasting righteousness shall reign in all the earth! For The King shall stand up, and all creation shall bow down! And He shall look upon the joy of His heart with gladness, and the blessing shall be fulfilled: _He shall bless them and keep them, and make His face to shine upon them; He shall be gracious to them, and lift up His countenance upon them, and grant them peace. {{ref:Numbers 6:24-26}}_\n\nAnd thus shall My name be placed upon the children of Israel, even upon all who have been grafted in, and they shall be blessed. Yea, they shall be exceedingly glad, dwelling in the presence of The Lord, forever!\n\nBehold, the multitudes shall break forth into singing! For The Glory of The Lord shall be alive in their hearts, the seal of The Living God shall be upon their foreheads, the Way of The Lord shall dwell in their limbs, and unending praise shall be upon their lips! All their doings shall bear fruit in righteousness, for The Law shall be written there, even in their innermost parts! And behold, The King of Peace shall overflow, and His people shall be satisfied and have rest, our joy complete."},{"align":"center","text":"Therefore, blessed are all those who seek\n\nForgiveness in YahuShua HaMashiach,\n\nAnd also receive."},{"align":"center","text":"For in His name shall all find freedom,\n\nSolace under the shadow of His healing wings..."},{"align":"center","text":"Life without end..."},{"align":"center","text":"Says The Lord God."}]},{"id":"bound-by-the-word","num":203,"title":"Bound by The Word","paragraphs":[{"align":"center","text":"And so The Word was sent,\n\nAnd came into the world\n\nTo seek and to save the lost."},{"align":"center","text":"And behold, He is coming again to deliver His own,\n\nAll those who believe and live by The Word;\n\nAnd to destroy those who fight against The Word,\n\nFor they too are bound by The Word."},{"align":"center","text":"For The Word stands forever, immovable and everlasting,\n\nUnchangeable, having complete authority over all things,\n\nThe light and the dark, the righteous and the wicked."},{"align":"center","text":"Indeed, the whole universe\n\nIs set within the confines of His will,\n\nGiving heed to Him who created it..."},{"align":"center","text":"Forever and ever...\n\nAmen."}]}];
